\id REV
\h REVELATION
\toc1 Matsh Haschu g Jesus Christ am i Maskogi John Wui
\toc2 REVELATION
\toc3 Rev
\mt1 Matsh Haschu g Jesus Christ am i Maskogi John Wui
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Hemu at am i tashogi g Jesus Christ hegai matsh haschu am hab wo e juh pi shaꞌi mehk iꞌajed. Jiosh ash am ahgid matsh am wo t-chehgi ahchim mach d piongaj. Tki heg am hema i kei g anghil. T id am ni-chehgi ahni John mani d piongaj g Jesus Christ.
\v 2 Kuni ia oꞌohan hegai mani haschu i neid. Ihda ni-oꞌohana o d Jiosh haꞌichu ahga ch d hegai wohokam mat am i maskogi g Jesus.
\v 3 Jiosh at wo wa s-ha hoꞌigeꞌel hegam mat am wo i neꞌokchul ch hegam mat ab wo kaihamad. E ash aihim mat am hab wo e juh wehs ihda gam hu baꞌich haꞌichu ahga mant in wo oꞌoha.
\s1 Oꞌohana am ha wui g wewaꞌak dakam Jesus Ihmdam
\p 
\v 4-5 Am ant wo i em-oꞌohani ahpim wewaꞌak dakam Jesus Christ ihmdam am Asia chekshani ch ed.
\p Ab at wo wa baꞌich i s-em-hoꞌigeꞌidad ch ab baꞌich wo i em-mahkad g i wehmtadag ch s-ap tahhadkam g t-ohg Jiosh ch Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag ch Jesus Christ. T-ohg Jiosh o chum hekid an haꞌichug. K g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag am wehmaj ch wewaꞌak masma e chehgidch am t-wehhejed. K g Jesus Christ si s-ap am i t-tashogid g wohokam ch d hegai mat si wehpeg ab uhpam s-ap i wuhsh ab muhkig amjed k am hahawa ha dahm g wehs kokownal id dahm jewed.
\p Ab o si t-tatchua ch heg hekaj e muhkid t-wehhejed k t-doꞌibia ab pi ap t-chuꞌijig amjed
\v 6 k hab t-juh mach d hahawa piongaj g t-ohg Jiosh ch am wo i ahgahid g haꞌichu ahgaj. Jesus Christ o wehs uꞌukch g gewkdag. Kutt ab wo ihmad chum hekid.
\p 
\v 7 Neh, e o aihim mat ep wo jiwia ab dahm kahchim amjed. Wehs hemajkam at wo neidad, chum wa hegam mat ab sisish kots t ab. Wehs nahnko mahs hemajkam at wo shoshani heg hekaj.
\p 
\v 8 T-kownalig Jiosh o wehs uꞌukch g gewkdag ch hab kaij, “Ahni ani d alpha ch d omega.” Idam o d si wehpeg ch si oidchkam oꞌohana. K hab ahg g Jiosh mo si wehpeg an haꞌichug ch si ha oidch an wabsh wo kia haꞌichugk.
\s1 Matsh g jesus am i e Maskogi John wui
\p 
\v 9 Dani em-wehm wohochuddam ahni John nach pi ab t-hemakochudch g Jesus Christ wehm. Ni am em-wehm apꞌedag Jiosh kownaltalig ed ch hekaj em-wehm ni-shoꞌigchud. An amt ni-wua heg ab al sikod jewed mo hab chehgig Patmos ch am haꞌichug shuhdagi ch ed nani wa pi si s-gewkam ahgahim g Jiosh neꞌoki ch hegai wohokam mat g Jesus am i tashogi.
\p 
\v 10 K am hu hebai d domig tash. Ni ab ihm g Jiosh. K g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag am si i ni-wehmaj. Kuni kah mat ab hema si s-kaidam neo ab ni-wehgaj k hab sha kaidag mat g kuikud ab ku
\v 11 k hab kaij, “An g oꞌohan mapt haschu wo i nei k am haha wo ha cheha mat am wo i bei ihda oꞌohana hegam ha wui wewaꞌak dakam Jesus ihmdam amai Ephesus t am ch Smyrna t am ch Pergamum t am ch Thyatira t am ch Sardis t am ch Philadelphia t am ch amai Laodicea t am.”
\p 
\v 12 Neh, nt ab si sikol i kekiwua mant wo nei mas hedai ab ni-wui neok k haha wabsh nei mo g wewaꞌak ohla lalampa an dadha chuhchakud t an.
\v 13 K am ha shahgid hema kehk ch hab mahs mo g Jiosh si Kehsha. K g lihwaj ged hu si ais g tahtdaj. K g ohla giwud an hab juhkch e bahsho.
\v 14 K g moꞌoj si s-tohta hab masma mo g s-wihs gew. K g wuhpuij si s-masma tonod hab masma mo g s-toni nahda.
\v 15 K g tahtdaj si s-wegima tonod hab masma mo g kohwli hahgig. K g neꞌokij hab masma hab kaidag mo g si geꞌe shuhdagi an med.
\v 16 Id o an uꞌukch g wewaꞌak huhuꞌu s-apko e-nowi ed ch an kamshch g is-pahyo. K id ab i wuhshanis chinij ab. K g wuhioshaj shaꞌi si tonod hab masma mo g tash tonlig dahm juhk.
\p 
\v 17 Kunt am i neidok ab i gei wecho hab sha masma mo g muhki.
\p Kut an ni-tahtam k hab kaij, “Pi g am shaꞌi ni-ehbenid. Dani ahni mani si wehpeg ia haꞌichug ch chum hekid ia wo haꞌichugk.
\v 18 Am ant wa chum ni-muhkid k uhpam ep ni-chegito k chum hekid d haha wo doakamk. Am ani dahm gewkdag g muhkig ch am dahm gewkdag amai mo am haꞌichug g koꞌi.
\p 
\v 19 “Pegih, am g oꞌohan map haschu i neid mat hab wo e juh hemu ch haschu hab wo e juh imhab i dahm.
\v 20 Am ant wo m-ahgi g s-aꞌagi haꞌichu ab amjed idam wewaꞌak huhuꞌu mani in uꞌukch ch idam wewaꞌak lalampa. Idam wewaꞌak lalampa o d hegam ni-ihmdam mo am kihdag hegam ha eda wewaꞌak kihhim. K idam wewaꞌak huhuꞌu o d ha-wanimeddam.”
\c 2
\s1 Oꞌohana am ha wui hegam mash am kihdag Ephesus t am
\p 
\v 1 K hab ep kaij ab ni-wui, “Am g oꞌohanid g ha wanimeddam hegam mo ab ni-ihm ch am kihdag Ephesus t am. Ihda ha wanimeddam at am wo ha ahgi mani hab kaij:
\p “Id o d haꞌichu ni-ahga ahni mani an ha uꞌukch g s-apkojed ni-nowikaj g wewaꞌak huhuꞌu ch an oimmed ha shahgid g wewaꞌak lalampa.
\v 2 S-mahch ani mam haschu hab junihim. S-ap am chikpan ch am wabsh s-e bahbgi ch pi ab hu shaꞌi ha bahbgi hegam mo ab ni-wui gegok. Haꞌi o hab chum kaij mo d ni-chuhchai. Kumt eda ha aꞌappem k s-mai mo d wabsh s-chu iꞌattomkam.
\v 3 Ab amt s-bahbagi nako g shoꞌigdag ni-wehhejed k pi shaꞌi haꞌasa.
\p 
\v 4 “Neh, id o s-ta hohhoꞌidama. K wabshaba haꞌichu pi ta hohhoꞌidama ab em-ab. Pi am ab hu ni-tatchua hemuch hab masma mam wa ged hu i heki hu.
\v 5 Am g wo i oidahim mamt heꞌesko i e mehkod ab ni-amjed k gam hu wo s-ohhod g pi ap e-chegitoi mamt hab ep wo masmak mam wa heki hu. Mtp sha pi gawul wo i e juh, nt gam hu wo i bei g em-tonligga.
\v 6 Id am hi wa s-ap am hab junihim mam si pi hohhoꞌid mo haschu s-ta edam hab junihim hegam mo am oid g Nicolas. Id o wa chum pi apko ha wanimed g Jiosh hemajkamga. Ahni ani hab waꞌap si pi hohhoꞌid ihda.
\p 
\v 7 “Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o am i maskogid g haꞌichu ni-ahga am em-wui ahpim mam ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag ha eꞌeda hegam wewaꞌak kihhim. Kumt wehsijj ab wo kaihamad. “Ab ant wo ha mah hegam mat gewito g pi apꞌekam g apꞌedag mat ab wo huh g bahidaj hegai uhs mo ab ha mahk g doakag ch am kehk Jiosh oidag ed.”
\s1 Oꞌohana am ha wui hegam mash am kihdag Smyrna t am
\p 
\v 8 K hab ep kaij ab ni-wui, “Am g oꞌohanid g ha wanimeddam hegam mo ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag Smyrna t am. Id at am wo ha ahgi mani hab kaij:
\p “Id o d haꞌichu ni-ahga ahni mani si wehpeg ia haꞌichug ch si ha oidch ia wabsh wo kia haꞌichugk, ahni mant muh k ep i wuhsh ab muhkig amjed.
\v 9 S-mahch ani mam e kudut. Dam hi wa chum shoꞌigkam iia ch wabshaba d s-kakais am Jiosh tahgio. S-mahch ani mo haꞌi si pi ap has em-ahg g Tutuligo. Idam o hab e elid mo d Jiosh hemajkamga ch eda wa chum pi woho no pi d wabsh Jiawul hemajkamga.
\p 
\v 10 “Pi g am wo shaꞌi ehbidad mamtp haschu i s-koꞌok ab wo nako. Neh, mt wo em-kuh. K wabshaba d wabsh Jiawul chiꞌoida ihda. Kut am waꞌi wehst-mahm tash hab wo mahsk ihda em-kudutadag. Am amt wo hihimad e-wohochudadag oidch am hugkam mamt hekid wo i koi. Kunt ab wo em-mah g pi ha huhugedam doakag hab masma mamt g gihko wo mah hegai mat wo ha gewito.
\p 
\v 11 “Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o am i maskogid g haꞌichu ni-ahga am em-wui ahpim mam ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag ha eꞌeda hegam wewaꞌak kihhim. Kumt wehsijj ab wo kaihamad.
\p “Hegam mat wo gewito g pi apꞌekam at pi wo ai g gokkokam muhkig.”
\s1 Oꞌohana am ha wui hegam mash am kihdag Pergamum t am
\p 
\v 12 K hab ep kaij ab ni-wui, “Am g oꞌohanid g ha wanimeddam hegam mo ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag Pergamum t am. T id am wo ha ahgi mani hab kaij:
\p “Id o d haꞌichu ni-ahga ahni mo g ni-is-pahyo ge aꞌaijed muꞌukasig.
\v 13 S-mahch ani mo g Jiawul himdag si s-gewkdag amai. M eda ab wabsh kia s-ni-mahch ch e ahg. Hegai mo d Antipas ch ab si s-ni-wohokamchud at wa e muhkid amai. Kumt eda wa pi shaꞌi ni-dagito.
\p 
\v 14 “K wabshaba am haꞌichu d hegai mani pi hohoꞌid am em-shahgid. Am o haꞌi em-wehmaj ch am hab wua hegai mat wa haschu ha mashcha g Tutuligo idam Balaambad ch Balakbad. Idam at wa ha mashcha mat wo huh hegai haꞌichu hugi mo wa ab e toꞌid g ha-jijoshchuda ch ehp mat hab wo wuad g s-tohntom haꞌichu. Id o wehs d pi apꞌekam am ni-tahgio.
\v 15 Am o haꞌi ep em-wehmaj mo g Nicolas mashchama ab s-wohochud.
\v 16 Gam g hu wo s-ohhod ihda pi apꞌekam. Nt wo em-cheggia heg hekaj is-pahyo mo ab i wuhshanis ni-chini amjed mamtp pi am hu wo i e apꞌech.
\p 
\v 17 “Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o am i maskogid g haꞌichu ni-ahga am em-wui ahpim mam ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag ha eꞌeda hegam wewaꞌak kihhim. Kumt wehsijj ab wo kaihamad.
\p “Ab ant wo ha mah hegam mat wo gewito g pi apꞌekam hegai pi ta behima haꞌichu hugi mo hab e aꞌaga ‘manna.’ Ab ant ep wo i ha mahkhi idam g s-toa Hodai. T hegam ha ab an wo oꞌohanask g wechij chehgig. T hegam wo waꞌi heheꞌejel s-mahchk g chehgig mat hedai i bei.”
\s1 Oꞌohana am ha wui hegam mash am kihdag Thyatira t am
\p 
\v 18 K hab ep kaij ab ni-wui, “Am g oꞌohanid g ha wanimeddam hegam mo ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag Thyatira t am. T id am wo ha ahgi mani hab kaij:
\p “Id o d ni-ahga ahni Jiosh alidag mo g ni-wuhpui hab masma tonod mo g nahda. K g ni-tahtad hab masma tohonnod mo g dahpiunas kohwli.
\v 19 S-mahch ani g s-apꞌekam em-chikpan, pihk em-elidadag, em-wohochudadag ch em-hemajimadadag ch em-bahbgidadag. Baꞌich am hab i e junihim iaꞌi idani.
\p 
\v 20 “K wabshaba am haꞌichu d hegai mani pi hohhoꞌid am em-shahgid. Am am wabsh hiwgid hegai uwi mo e wepogid g Jezebelbad ch hab e aꞌaga mo d Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam. Id o ha mashcham g ni-ihmdam mat am hab wo junihid g pi apꞌekam haꞌichu ab aꞌai e wehm ch ep wo koꞌad hegai haꞌichu hugi mo ab e toꞌid g ha-jijoshchuda.
\v 21 Ab ant wa heꞌes i mah g tash mat gam hu wo s-ohhod g pi ap e-chegitoi. K wabshaba pi hohhoꞌid mat wo dagito g pi apꞌekam.
\v 22 Kunt heg hekaj hab wo juh mat wo mumku k wo woꞌiwua. T hegam chechoj mo am wehmaj wohppo am wehmaj ep wo e shoꞌigch. S-hohtam ant hab wo juh ihda heg hi wa matp gam hu wo s-ohhod g pi ap e-chegitoi.
\v 23 Nt wo ha kokda g mahmdaj mat wehs g ni-ihmdam wo s-mai mani s-mahch g hemajkam ha-chegitoidag ch ha-tatchuidag. Ab ant wo em-namkid heg hekaj mam haschu has i junihim.
\p 
\v 24 “Haꞌijj ahpim Thyatira t am hemajkam amt pi am hu i oi ihda pi apꞌekam mashchamadag k pi mai hegai mo haꞌijj hab aꞌaga ‘Jiawul si s-juhk s-aꞌagi haꞌichu.’ Pi ant ab hu baꞌich haꞌichu s-wehch wo em-mohtoꞌi.
\v 25 Mt wabshaba hemho wa wo s-wihnam uꞌukchid hegai mam haschu i edgid ch ab wo ai mant wo uhpam jiwia.
\p 
\v 26-28 “Ni-ohg Jiosh at ab ni-mah g gewkdag mant wehs s-gewkam wo ha dahmkad g jejewed ch wo ha padch g pi apꞌekam kokownaltalig. Kunt ab wo ha mah ihda gewkdag hegam mat wo gewito g pi apꞌekam k am hab wo junihid g ni-tatchui ch ab wo ai mant ep wo jiwia. T am ni-wehm wo ha dahmkad g jejewed. Kut am ha wehhejed wo mahsi g hoꞌigeꞌidadag hab masma mat g s-mahs huꞌu.
\p 
\v 29 “Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o am i maskogid g haꞌichu ni-ahga am em-wui ahpim mam ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag ha eꞌeda hegam wewaꞌak kihhim. Kumt wehsijj ab wo kaihamad.”
\c 3
\s1 Oꞌohana am ha wui hegam mash am kihdag Sardis t am
\p 
\v 1 K hab ep kaij ab ni-wui, “Am g oꞌohanid g ha wanimeddam hegam mo ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag Sardis t am. T heg am wo ha ahgi mani hab kaij:
\p “Id o d haꞌichu ni-ahga ahni mani an uꞌukch g wewaꞌak huhuꞌu ch am kehshch g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag mat wewaꞌak masma wo e chehgidad em-wehhejed. S-mahch ani mam has chuꞌig. Bam em-elid mam d s-apꞌekam. Mt eda e mehkod ab ni-amjed.
\v 2 Neh, mt ab wo i nehnen k ab wo i gewkai hegai mam haschu wabsh kia edgid mat koi wo s-ap muh. Pi o hohhoꞌid g Jiosh hegai mam haschu am hab junihim.
\v 3 Am g wo s-chegitok mam wa haschu ab em-mashcham k ab wo i s-wohog elid k gam hu wo s-ohhod g pi ap e-chegitoi. Kumtp pi wo sha nehnen, nt s-aꞌagi ia wo jiwia hab sha masma mo g s-chu ehskam. Kumt pi wo shaꞌi mahchk g ohla mant hekid wo i jiwia.
\p 
\v 4 “Haꞌijj ahpim amai Sardis t am am hi wa si e nuhkud mat pi haꞌichu wo em-uamhu. Ahpim mam s-ap am hab e junihim amt ni-wehm wo himad s-tohtam e enidadadch.
\v 5 Hegam mat hedai wo gewito g pi apꞌekam at s-tohtam wo e enigadad. An o oꞌohadag g ha-chechgig an dahm kahchim ch ed mo d e doꞌibiakam. Kunt pi wo shaꞌi oa g ha chechgig k wabshaba hab wo chei am tahgio g ni-ohg Jiosh ch am ha tahgio g anghiligaj mo d ni-hemajkamga.
\p 
\v 6 “Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o am i maskogid g haꞌichu ni-ahga am em-wui ahpim mam ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag ha eꞌeda hegam wewaꞌak kihhim. Kumt wehsijj ab wo kaihamad.”
\s1 Oꞌohana am ha wui hegam mash am kihdag Philadelphia t am
\p 
\v 7 K hab ep kaij ab ni-wui, “Am g oꞌohanid g ha wanimeddam hegam mo ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag Philadelphia t am. T heg am wo ha ahgi mani hab kaij:
\p “Id o d haꞌichu ni-ahga ahni mani d hekia s-apꞌekam ch d wohokam ch an uꞌukch g Davidbad yahwi. Id ani hekaj haꞌichu kukpiꞌok. T pi hedai wo e nako mas ab ep wo kuh. Kuni haꞌichu kukpa. T pi hedai wo e nako mas ab ep wo kuhpiꞌo.
\v 8 S-mahch ani mam pi am hu i si s-gewpkdag ch wabshaba am oidch hab e junihim g ni-mashchama ch ab si ni-hiwig. Ab ant i hema kuhpiꞌo g kihjeg em-wehhejed. T pi hedai wo e nako mas ab ep wo kuh.
\p 
\v 9 “Haꞌi o hab e aꞌaga mo d Tutuligo ch d Jiosh hemajkamga. K eda hab chuꞌig mo d wabsh Jiawul hemajkamga. Bant wo ha juh mat ab wo i hihi em-wui k ab wo i shulig k ab wo si has i em-el. T wo wehsijj s-mai mani ahpim ab si em-tatchua.
\p 
\v 10 “Am am hab junihim g ni-chehanig ch s-bahbgim ab nakog haꞌichu. Nt heg hekaj wo em-nuhkud heg amjed kudutadag mo ab him ha wui g wehs hemajkam mat am wo ha aꞌappe wehs jewed shuhdgim.
\v 11 S-hohtam ant wo jiwia. Am g wo si nuhkud hegai mani ab em-mahkch. T hab pi hedai wo shaꞌi em-wohppoꞌi hegai mani ab em-makiog hahawa.
\p 
\v 12 “Bant wo ha juh hegam mat wo gewito g pi apꞌekam mat d wo uꞌugchuk am Jiosh kihdag ed hab sha masma mo g che-tondag am geꞌe cheopi ed. Kut idam pi hekid wo shaꞌi dagito g Jiosh kihdag. An ant ha ab wo oꞌoha g ni-Jioshga chehgig ch g Jiosh kihhim chehgig. Jiosh kihhim o d Wechij Jerusalem ch ab wo i hud Jiosh amjed an dahm kahchim ch ed. Ab ant ha ab ep wo oꞌoha g ni-wechij chehgig.
\p 
\v 13 “Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o am i maskogid g haꞌichu ni-ahga am em-wui ahpim mam ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag ha eꞌeda hegam wewaꞌak kihhim. Kumt wehsijj ab wo kaihamad.”
\s1 Oꞌohana am ha wui hegam mash am kihdag Laodicea t am
\p 
\v 14 K hab ep kaij ab ni-wui, “Am g oꞌohanid g ha wanimeddam hegam mo ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag Laodicea t am. T heg am wo ha ahgi mani hab kaij:
\p “Id o d haꞌichu ni-ahga ahni mani s-ap wohokamchud g wohokam ab amjed g Jiosh ch am wehs dahm g Jiosh nahtoi.
\v 15 S-mahch ani mam has chuꞌig. Bam chum e elid mam s-ap ab ihm g Jiosh. Kum eda pi am hu woho i e dagitokch wui.
\v 16 Nt heg hekaj gam hu hab wo i em-juh ab ni-amjed hab sha masma mamt gam hu wo wiho g wabsh s-huhk wasib.
\v 17 Bam chechꞌe mo am wabsh i s-em-apꞌe haꞌichu nam pi d s-kakais ch hab ep chechꞌe mam pi haꞌichu ep shaꞌi tatchua. Ni wabshaba em-ahgid mam si shoꞌig ch s-ta hoꞌigeꞌidama ch gm wabsh i s-dadpk ch pi nenea.
\v 18 Ab g wo i e dagito ni-wui k hab masma wo edagi g s-wohom kaisdag ch s-kehg wehschuga ch kulani am wehhejed g em-wuhpui. Kumt hahawa pi wo shoꞌigk ch pi wo s-dadpk ch wo s-neneak.
\v 19 Haꞌichu ani shohbid ch ha gewittan hegam mani ab si ha tatchua mat hekaj gam hu wo s-ohhod g pi ap e-chegitoi.
\p 
\v 20 “Neh, ab ani em-waid ni-wui. K heg wa wepo mani ab kehk em-kihjeg ab ch ab shontpag ch ab em-chehcheg. Kumt wo kah mani ab neok k wo i kuhpiꞌo g kihjeg. Nt ab wo i wah. Kutt ab aꞌai wo t-ihmad ch t-wehm wo si s-hehgigk hab masma matt hems wo t-wehm t-gegosidad.
\v 21 Ni-ohg Jiosh at an ni-dai e-hugid an kownal ni-daikud an nant pi gewito g pi apꞌekam. Kunt ahni am hab waꞌap wo em-dai ni-hugid an kownal daikud t ab mamtp hedai wo gewito g pi apꞌekam.
\p 
\v 22 “Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o am i maskogid g haꞌichu ni-ahga am em-wui ahpim mam ab si ni-hiwig ch am kihdag ha eꞌeda hegam wewaꞌak kihhim. Kumt wehsijj ab wo kaihamad.”
\c 4
\s1 Mam has masma ab si has elid g Jiosh an dahm kahchim ch ed
\p 
\v 1 Ab ant hahawa i nen k haꞌichu ep neid. Am ni-tahgio o hab sha mahs mo ab kuhpiꞌokas g dahm kahchim hab sha masma mo ab ge kihjeg.
\p Kuni ep kah g neꞌokij g Jesus. K hab sha kaidag mo g kuikud ch hab kaij ab ni-wui, “Ab g i hihm. Nt am wo m-chehgi mat haschu hemho wa am hab wo e juh iꞌajed imhab.”
\p 
\v 2 T ha hekaj ab si i ni-wehmt g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag. K shahag wepo mat g dahm kahchim am e chehgi ni-wui. Kuki g geꞌe kownal daikud ab kehk. K an hema daha id ab.
\v 3 K g wuhioshaj wabsh tonod hab masma mo hegam si s-kehg hohodai mo hab e aꞌaga ‘jasper’ ch ‘carnelian.’ K an kownal daikud wehgaj hab chuꞌig g kiohod. K id s-chehdagi hab masma mo hegai s-kehg hodai mo hab e aꞌaga ‘emerald.’
\v 4 Kuki an wehgaj hab ep chuꞌig g gokko gamai giꞌik kownal dadaikud. Kuki an ha ab dadha g gokko gamai giꞌik geꞌeged ch s-tohtakaj e enigadadch ch g ohla gigiko ab wahpkch.
\v 5 Kuki ab geꞌe kownal daikud amjed ab si memhe g wepgi. Kuki ab toahim g tataniki. Kuki g wewaꞌak kuhchki am memeihim baꞌich g geꞌe kownal daikud no pi g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag wewaꞌak masma e chehgidch am t-wehhejed.
\v 6 Am baꞌich g geꞌe kownal daikud oki shaꞌi si s-dahpk ch hab masma mo g mi-lihda am tadani ch am wabsh gai tonod.
\p An wehgaj g kownal daikud oki an aꞌai gegok g giꞌik haꞌichu dodakam ch wehsko wuhpui.
\v 7 K hema hab sha mahs mo g mawid. K hema hab ep mahs mo g wisilo. K hema g wuhioshaj hab mahs mo g oꞌodham wuhiosha. K hema hab mahs mo g baꞌag ch an daꞌa.
\v 8 K wehsijj idam chuhdp aꞌan. K g ha-aꞌan wehsko wuhpui. K chum hekid neꞌe hab masma:
\q1 “Ab ach si has elid g t-kownalig Jiosh.
\q1 Do si hekia s-apꞌekam ch si s-gewkdag ch chum hekid an haꞌichug.”
\m 
\v 9 Kuki am neꞌe idam giꞌik haꞌichu dodakam ch ab mahk g has elida ch hoꞌigeꞌelig hegai mo chum hekid an haꞌichug ch an da kownal daikud t an.
\v 10 K heg wui ab hab waꞌap i shuhullig hegam geꞌeged ch am wuashulig g e-gigiko ch am wecho shuhullig ch ab ihm ch hab chechꞌe:
\q1 
\v 11 “T-kownalig Jiosh, ab ap apꞌedag matt ab wo si m-hehgchulidad ch ab wo si has m-elidad nap pi wehs s-gewkdag ch wehs haꞌichu nahto.
\q1 K hab d m-elida mo in hab chuꞌig.”
\c 5
\s1 Mash g holiwek oꞌohana ch kahwal mad neid
\p 
\v 1 Ni haha wabsh neid. Kuki an uꞌukch g holiwek oꞌohana s-apkojed e-nowi ed hegai mo an da kownal daikud t an. K wehsko oꞌohanas ab ab ihda ch wewaꞌakpa ab si bidshpi ch cheposidas.
\p 
\v 2 Neid ani ehp g si s-gewk anghil. K heg si s-kaidam amog ch hab kaij, “Dohꞌo am hugkam apꞌedag mat wo e nako mat wo wantsh g chechposig k ab wo i kuhpiꞌo ihda oꞌohana?”
\p 
\v 3 T wabshaba pi hedai e cheh an dahm kahchim ch ed ch in jewed dahm ch am jewed wecho mat wo e nakog k wo kuhpiꞌo k an wo i nei eda g oꞌohana.
\v 4 Ni heg hekaj si pi ap ni-tahtk ch shoak.
\p 
\v 5 K hab hahawa kaij hema hegam geꞌeged ab ni-wui, “Pi g am shoakad. Neh, Mawid Namkam at gewito g pi apꞌekam k hab wo e nako mat wo wantsh g wewaꞌak chechposig k ab wo i kuhpiꞌo g holiwek oꞌohana. Bo masma hab chuꞌig mo hab masma oꞌohadag mo id ab d Judabad amjedkam ch d ep Davidbad amjedkam.”
\p 
\v 6 Kuni hahawa neid hegai moki hab ahg. K eda ihda Mawid Namkam hab masma ab i e chehgidch mo g kahwal mad ch atki heki hu e muhkid k idani am kehk si eda g kownal daikud. K an wehgaj gegok hegam giꞌik haꞌichu dodakam ch hegam geꞌeged. K hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch wewaꞌak aꞌag ch wewaꞌak wuhpui. Idam wewaꞌak wuhpui o hab d ahga mat ab amjed i hih g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag k an wehsko neid ch nuhkud g Jiosh nahtoi.
\v 7 T am hih hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch k am bei g holiwek oꞌohana ab s-apko nowij ab hegai mo ab da kownal daikud t ab.
\v 8 T ha hekaj ab wui i shul hegam giꞌik haꞌichu doakam ch hegam gokko gamai giꞌik geꞌeged. K idam wehsijj ge ahlipa ch ohla hohas-hahaꞌa. K hegam ha eda hohas-hahaꞌa s-ap uhw shuhdagi ch id d ha-hoꞌigeꞌidahuna g Jiosh hemajkamga.
\v 9 K am hema aꞌaga g wechij neꞌi. K g ha-neꞌi hab chuꞌig:
\q1 “Ahpi ap geꞌe apꞌedag mapt wo e nakog k am wo bei g holiwek oꞌohana k wo wantsh g chechposigaj napt pi e muhkid k hekaj ab uhpam i ha ui g hemajkam am wehhejed g Jiosh.
\q1 K g m-uꞌi d wehsko dakam hemajkam ch d nahnko kaidam neneokdam ab wehs jejewed ha amjed.
\q1 
\v 10 Bapt ha juh mat wehs d wo papalk ch ab wo ihmad g Jiosh ch d wo kokownalk wehsko jewed dahm.”
\p 
\v 11 Nt am hahawa nea k ha kah muꞌi mihl anghil. Idam o an wehgaj gegok g geꞌe kownal daikud am ha wehm hegam giꞌik haꞌichu doakam ch hegam geꞌeged
\v 12 ch si s-kaidam neꞌe hab masma:
\q1 “Hegai mat kahwalkaj e muhkid o ab ab ulini mamt am wo i kei wehs haꞌichu dahm k ab wehs wo mah g s-kaisdag ch haꞌichu amichudadag ch gewkdag ch ab has elidadag ch hehgchulidadag ch hoꞌigeꞌidadag.”
\m 
\v 13 Kuni ha kah g wehs haꞌichu doakam an dahm kahchim ch ed ch an jewed dahm ch am jewed wecho ch am geꞌe kahchki ch ed. Wehs idam o am neꞌe hab masma:
\q1 “Do ha wuikam g Jiosh heg wehm mat kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch mamb ab wo si pihk e elidad ha wui ch ab wo si has ha elidad ch ab wo ha hehgchulidad ch ab ha wui wo dagitokchid g e-gewkdag chum hekid.”
\m 
\v 14 Tki hegam giꞌik haꞌichu doakam ab wohokamchud k hab kaij, “Am o wa woho ihda.” T g geꞌeged ab i shul wecho k ab si ihm.
\c 6
\s1 Matsh ab wo i e kuhkpiꞌo g chechposig
\p 
\v 1 Ni ab neid hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. Kutki hema gam wantsh hegam wewaꞌak chechposig. K hema hab kaij hegam giꞌik haꞌichu doakam, “Ab g i hihm.”
\v 2 K g neꞌokij hab sha kaidag mo g tataniki. Nt hahawa ep chum nei. Tki g s-toa kawyu am hema i wuhsh. Kuki ab hema cheshaj ch g gaht uꞌa. Mt g gihko an hab juh moꞌoj an. Ge oki gewkdag ch am i wuhsh mat wo ha gewito g hemajkam.
\p 
\v 3 Kutki am hahawa ab kuhpiꞌo g gokkokam cheposig hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. Kuni kah g gokkokam haꞌichu doakam. K hab kaij, “Ab g i hihm.”
\v 4 Tki ab hema ep i wuhsh g kawyu k ge s-wegi. K ab hema cheshaj. Kumt ab mah g gewkdag mat hab wo juh g cheggiadag an jewed dahm mat g hemajkam wo aꞌai e kokda. Kumt g geꞌe is-pahyo ab mah.
\p 
\v 5 Tki ab hahawa i kuhpiꞌo g waikkokam cheposig hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. Kuni kah g waikkokam haꞌichu doakam. K hab kaij, “Ab g i hihm.” Nt chum nei. T g s-chuk kawyu ab i wuhsh. K hema cheshaj ch g pisaltakud uꞌa.
\v 6 K am hema neok ab ha shahgid hegam giꞌik haꞌichu doakam ch hab kaij, “T wo si s-namkigk g haꞌichu hugi. Mt chum hems wo ha namkid g e-nahtoi am chikpank hemako tashkaj mamt wo ha nolawt g al hemako s-wehch pilkani o g waik s-wehch si-wahyo. Mt wabshaba pi wo shohbi g manjeki ch nawait.”
\p 
\v 7 Tki gam hahawa wantsh k kuhpiꞌo g giꞌikkokam cheposig hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. Ni kah g giꞌikkokam haꞌichu doakam. K hab kaij, “I hihm.”
\v 8 Nt ab i chum nei. Tki g s-kohmagi kawyu ab i wuhsh. Kuki hema cheshaj ch hab chehgig Muhki. Kuki ab si mia oidch him hegai mash hab e aꞌaga Jiawul Kih. Mtki idam ab ha mah g gewkdag am dahm g hemako tahpani mo giꞌikko e tahpanch (¼) ihda jewed. Kutki ha kokda cheggiadag ch ed ch g bihugigkaj ch mumkidagkaj. Tki g mischini haꞌichu doakam hab waꞌap haꞌi wo ha kokda.
\p 
\v 9 Tki gam hahawa ep wantsh k kuhpiꞌo g hetaspokam cheposig hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. Kuni neid ab wecho g iagchulidakud g ha-dodakag hegam matki e koꞌij heg hekaj mo am ahgahim g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga ch pi shaꞌi dagito g haꞌichu e ahga.
\v 10 Idam o si s-kaidam hihnk ch hab kaij, “Si s-gewkam kownal ch si s-apꞌekam ch si s-wohokam, heꞌes at wo i tashk mapt haha wo ha lodai g hemajkam an jewed dahm k ab wo ha mah g s-koꞌok namkidadag heg hekaj mat t-kokda?”
\p 
\v 11 Mt ab hahawa wehsijj i ha mahkhi g s-tohta liliwa k hab ha ahg mat wo shaꞌal baꞌich i e uhꞌulinihogid k ab wo ai mat wehs wo e koꞌij hegam ha wehm pion ch ha-wepnag mat ha wepo masma wo e koꞌij.
\p 
\v 12 Tki gam hahawa ep wantsh k kuhpiꞌo g chuhdpokam cheposig hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. Tki am shaꞌi si uꞌugij g jewed. Kutki g tash ge chuku hab masma mo g s-kowk s-chuk ikus. Kutki g mashad wehsko ge wegih hab masma mo g ehꞌed.
\v 13 Tki g huhuꞌu i shul ab dahm kahchim amjed an jewed dahm hab sha masma mat g pi bakam suhna wo i shul ab e-jehj amjed mat g s-gewk hewel wo si uꞌugij.
\v 14 Tki g dahm kahchim ab wabsh i huhug hab sha masma mat g tapial wo i e holiwkad k ged hu wo e cheh. Tki wehs g dohdaꞌag ch g al siꞌiskod jejewed am shuhdagi ch ed gam hu gawulko i e uhꞌul.
\p 
\v 15 Ni ha neid matki wehs chum e eꞌesto g hemajkam, chum hems g kokownal ch si s-has hahaꞌichu ch shondal ha-geꞌegeꞌejig ch s-gewpkkam ch hegam ehp mo d shoꞌigkam ch hegam mo d nenehol. Am atki chum e eꞌesto chehcho ch ed ch am hohodai wepcho
\v 16 ch ab si hihnk dohdaꞌag ch hohodai wui hab kaijch, “Ab g wo i shulig t-dahm mat pi wo t-neidad g Jiosh. Oi g wo t-eꞌesto ab amjed hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch mat pi wo s-koꞌokam t-namkid.
\v 17 E o aihim g lodaita tash. Kutt pi wo shaꞌi t-nako matt ab wui wo gegokiwua.”
\c 7
\s1 Matsh muꞌi Tutuligo wo e doꞌibia
\p 
\v 1 Ntki haha wabsh ha nei g giꞌik anghil. K hema ab kehk siꞌalig tahgio ch hema ab huduni tahgio ch hema ab wakolim tahgio k ch hema ab juhpin tahgio. Kuki idam an uꞌukch g giꞌik hewel mat pi an hu wo hewedad jewed dahm o an kahchki dahm. Kuki gam hu wabsh i pi hoini wehs haꞌichu.
\p 
\v 2 Kuni hahawa hema ep neid g anghil. Kuki id ab him siꞌal wecho amjed ch g Jiosh cheposidakud uꞌa. Kuki eda ab mahks hegam giꞌik mat wo padch g jewed ch kahchki. K wabshaba ihda hema ab ha wui hab kaij.
\v 3 “Pi g am s-koꞌokam has wo juhni g jewed ch kahchki ch kukui. Kutt ab hoꞌip kia ha chepos g Jiosh pionag ab ha-koka ab.”
\p 
\v 4 Kuni kah mash d siant giꞌikko wehst-mahm gamai giꞌik mihl (144,000) hegam mamt ha chepos heg hekaj Jiosh cheposidakud.
\v 5 Am o haꞌichug g gamai gohk mihl (12,000) ab wehsijj i ha amjed g t-shohshonbad. Idam o wa d gamai gohk ch wa hab chechgig Judah, Reuben, Gad,
\v 6 Asher, Naphtali, Manasseh,
\v 7 Simeon, Levi, Issachar,
\v 8 Zebulun, Joseph, Benjamin.
\s1 Si geꞌe hemapda
\p 
\v 9 Ntki hahawa ep ha nei moki am shaꞌi si geꞌe hemapig hab chuꞌig. Kuki pi ta kuintama idam hemajkam ch ab amjed g wehsko jejewed ch d nahnko mahs oꞌodham ch nahnko kaidam neneokdam.
\p Kuki am daha e-kownal daikud ab hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. Kuki hegam muꞌi hemajkam am baꞌich gegok ch s-tohtakaj e enigadadch ch g haꞌichu iꞌibhonig an uhꞌukch
\v 10 ch si s-kaidam neneok ch hab kaij:
\q1 “T-doꞌibiadag o ab amjed g Jiosh ch ab amjed hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch.”
\p 
\v 11 Kuki wehsijj g anghil an ha wehgaj gegok ch am i shulig ch ab ihm g Jiosh ch hab ep kaij:
\q1 
\v 12 “Ab ach si hoꞌigeꞌid ch si hehgchulid g Jiosh no pi wehs edgid g amichudadag ch gewkdag chum hekid.
\q1 Amen.”
\p 
\v 13 Tki hema hegam geꞌeged ab ni-kakke k hab kaij, “Dohꞌo wud idam hemajkam mo s-tohtam e enigadadch ch hebai amjed hihim?”
\p 
\v 14 Ni hab kaij ab wui, “Pi ani shaꞌi mahch. Ahpi ap wa s-mahch.”
\p K hab kaij ab ni-wui, “Idam o d hegam mat ab s-ap gahi wuwha g si geꞌe shoꞌigchudadag. Heg o wa wepo mat am i wapko g e-wepschuga heg hekaj ehꞌedaj hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch.
\q1 
\v 15 Heg o hekaj ia gegok Jiosh baꞌich ch ab ihm wehs tashkaj ch s-chuhugam oidk.
\q1 Kut g Jiosh wo ha nuhkudad chum hekid.
\q1 
\v 16 Pi at dahm d ep wo bihugkoik o d wo tonkkoik.
\q1 Pi at hekid ep wo s-tonik ha wehhejed.
\q1 
\v 17 Hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch at wo ha nuhkudad hab masma mo g kahwal nuhkuddam ch am wo i ha wanim heg wui s-kehg doakag mo heg wepogidas shonkam shuhdagi.
\q1 Kut g Jiosh ab wehs wo i oa g ha-ohꞌog.”
\c 8
\s1 Matsh gam i e wantsh g wewaꞌakkokam cheposig
\p 
\v 1 Tki am hahawa wantsh k kuhpiꞌo g wewaꞌakkokam cheposig hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. Kuki gam hu wabsh i pi shahmuni an dahm kahchim ch ed am huꞌi eda hugkam ohla.
\p 
\v 2 Kuni haha wabsh ha neid hegam wewaꞌak anghil moki am gegok Jiosh tahgio. Mtki idam ab i ha mahkhi g wewaꞌak kukuikud.
\p 
\v 3 Kuki am kehk g iagchulidakud kownal daikud baꞌich. Tki heg wui am hema ep jiwia g anghil k g ohla haꞌa uꞌa. Kumtki am eda geꞌe toꞌi g s-ap uhwchu mat ab wo i wehnad g ha-hoꞌigeꞌidalig g Jiosh hemajkamga k am wo iagchul Jiosh wui.
\v 4 Kutki g anghil mehi g s-ap uhwchu. Tki g kuhbs ab amjed am uhgk i chesh wehnadk g ha-hoꞌigeꞌidalig g hemajkam.
\v 5 Tki am hahawa bei g mehi ab amjed g iagchulidakud heg hekaj ohla haꞌa k am iawua jewed dahm. Kutki am shaꞌi si kop g tataniki k si s-kaidag. Kuki g wepgi an tohonnod ch g jewed si uꞌugij.
\s1 Matsh am wo e kuhu g kukuikud
\p 
\v 6 Tki hegam wewaꞌak anghil mo uꞌa g wewaꞌak kukuikud am i e nako mat wo ku.
\p 
\v 7 Tki g wehpeg anghil am si kuhu g e-kuikudkaj. Tki g chea ch mehi wehnadch g ehꞌed ab i e iawua an dahm g jewed. Kutki hemako tahpani mei g jewed mo waik e tahpanch (⅓). Kutki g kukui hab waꞌap masma haꞌas meitto. Tki g washai wehs meitto.
\p 
\v 8 Tki g gokkokam anghil am hahawa epai kuhu g e-kuikudkaj. Tki am haꞌichu e daꞌich ge shuhdagi ch ed ch hab sha mahs mo g ge geꞌe doꞌag ch meihim. Tki hemako tahpani mo waik e tahpanch g ge shuhdagi wabsh e ehꞌedch.
\v 9 Tki haꞌakia ep koi g haꞌichu doakam am ge shuhdagi ch ed ch haꞌakia ep wachkk g wapalko am shuhdagi ch ed.
\p 
\v 10 Tki g waikkokam anghil am hahawa ep ku. Tki g geꞌe huꞌu ab i gei dahm kahchim t amjed k hab masma meihim mo g kuhchki ch maꞌish g hemako tahpani mo waik e tahpanch g aꞌakimel ch shohshonkam shuhdagi.
\v 11 K hab chehgig ihda huꞌu S-siwkam. Kutki g hemako tahpani mo waik e tahpanch g shuhdagi wabsh ge siwa. Tki muꞌi hemajkam koi chum iꞌik ihda shuhdagi no pi si s-siw.
\p 
\v 12 Tki g giꞌikkokam anghil am hahawa epai kuhu g e-kuikudkaj. Kutki g hemako tahpani mo waik e tahpanch g tash ch mashad ch huhuꞌu ge chuku. Kutki heg hekaj haꞌas huhug g ha-tonlig ch haꞌas tash pi tonod tash oidam ch chuhug oidam.
\p 
\v 13 Nt am hahawa ep i nen k kah. Kuki si s-kaidam hab kaij g baꞌag an uhgk daꞌadch, “Eh, si s-ta ehbidama! Dat wo si s-ta ehbidamak am ha wehhejed hegam mo an kih jewed dahm mat ab wo kaida g kuikud ab ha amjed hegam waik anghil mat am ep wo kuhk.”
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Tki am hahawa ep kuhu g hetaspokam anghil g e-kuikudkaj. Kuni neid g huꞌu. Tki id am gei jewed dahm ab dahm kahchim t amjed. Kumtki ab mah hegai yahwi mo heg d wuikam wag mo pi hebai hug.
\v 2 Kutki ihda huꞌu am kuhpiꞌo hegai wag. Tki g kuhbs hab masma ab i wuhsh mo ab amjed g si geꞌe nahdakud. Kutki g tash tonlig wabsh wehsko chuku heg hekaj kuhbs ab amjed g wag.
\v 3 Tki g geꞌeged shoshꞌo ab i huhud amjed g kuhbs an dahm g jewed. Kumtki ab ha mah g gewkdag mat s-koꞌokam wo ha juh hab masma mo g nanakshel.
\v 4 Kum hab ha ahg mat pi wo koꞌokam has juh g washai ch kukui ch wehs haꞌichu wuhshanig. Hegam atsh wo waꞌi s-koꞌokam has ha juh hemajkam mo pi ab hu cheposidas e-koka ab heg hekaj Jiosh cheposidakud.
\v 5 Kumtki pi ha hiwigi idam shoshꞌo mat wo ha kokda idam hemajkam k wabshaba wabsh wo s-koꞌokam ha shoꞌigch hetasp mashad ab. Kuki g s-koꞌok ab amjed g ha-shoꞌigchuda hab masma s-koꞌok mo g nakshel keꞌi.
\v 6 Kutki heg oidam hetasp mashad idam hemajkam wo chum si s-koꞌim k wabshaba pi wo koi.
\p 
\v 7 Kuki idam shoshꞌo hab mams mo hegam kakawyu mo e hekaj am cheggiadag ch ed. Kuki g ha-mohmi hab mams mo g uꞌuwi ha-mohmi. K an ha-mohmi an wahpkch g ohla gigiko.
\v 8 Kuki g ha-wuhpiosha sha oꞌodham ha-wuhpiosha mams. Kuki g ha-tahtami hab mams mo g mawid tahtami.
\v 9 Kuki g ha-babsho ab haꞌichukaj mamꞌaishch mo hab sha mams mo g wainomi koktoni. K g ha-aꞌan hab sha kaidag mo g muꞌi cheggiakud kakalit an wohpo mat wo ha cheggia.
\v 10 Kuki g ha-bahbhai ch ha-uꞌush hab mams mo g nanakshel ha-uꞌush. K g e-bahbhaikaj e nakog mat wo s-koꞌokam has ha juh g hemajkam hetasp mashad ab.
\v 11 Kuki ep ge kownalig. K id am ha wanimed ch d hegai anghil mo nuhkud g s-juhk wag ch hab chehgig am t-neꞌoki ed Abbadon k ch am Greek ha-neꞌoki ed hab chehgig Apollyon. K id hab d ahga Haꞌichu Padchuddam.
\p 
\v 12 Tki am i huhug ihda wehpeg si s-ta ehbidam haꞌichu. K id i dahm matki am hab ep wo e juh g gohk si s-ta ehbidam haꞌichu.
\p 
\v 13 Tki g chuhdpokam anghil am hahawa epai kuhu g e-kuikudkaj. Kuni kah mo ab hema neok ab chuhchpulij amjed hegai ohla iagchulidakud mo am kehk baꞌich g Jiosh.
\v 14 K hegai mo ab neok hab kaij heg wui anghil mo d chuhdpokam ch an uꞌukch g kuikud, “Ha g dagito hegam giꞌik anghil mo am e wupulshch heg bahsho akimel mo hab chehgig Euphrates.”
\p 
\v 15 Mtki am i ha dagito idam giꞌik anghil. Idam oki wa e nahtokch id si wehhejed ohla id si tash ed id si mashad ab ch id si ahidag ed mat wo ha kokda g hemako tahpani mo waik e tahpanch wehs hemajkam.
\v 16 Kum am ni-ahgid mash d gohk siant mi-yohn (200,000,000) idam mo g kakawyu ha chehchejch.
\p 
\v 17 Kuni am ni-tahgio neid g kakawyu ch hegam mo ha chehchejch. Kuki g ha-wainomi koktoni si s-wepegi ch ep s-oꞌam ch hab masma s-chehedagi mo g dahm kahchim. K g kakawyu ha-mohmi hab mams mo g maipid ha-mohmi. K ab ha-chihchini amjed ab i wuhshani g mei ch kuhbs ch s-uam uhw.
\v 18 Tki g hemako tahpani mo waik e tahpanch g hemajkam e koꞌij id hekaj waik haꞌichu mo ab wuhshani ha-chihchini amjed.
\v 19 Kuki idam kakawyu hab waꞌap s-gewpkdag am ha bahbhai am. Ha-bahbhai oki hab mams mo g kohkꞌoi ch ab ge mohmi. K id hekaj s-koꞌokam has ha wua.
\p 
\v 20 Kutki wabshaba hegam hemajkam mat an wih pi gam hu s-ohhod g pi ap e-chuꞌijig k ab wabsh kia ha ihm g jijawul ch ab ep ha ihm g e-jijoshchuda. Kuki eda ihda pi am hu haꞌichu d i ha-wehmtadag. Ha-jijoshchuda o d wabsh haꞌichu ha-nahtoi ch pi haꞌichu neid ch pi haꞌichu kah ch pi shaꞌi oiopo no pi d wabsh ohla ch plahda ch kohwli ch hodai ch uhs.
\v 21 Idam hemajkam atki pi shaꞌi dagito g e-muꞌadag ch e-hihoina ch haꞌichu ehsig ch hegai mo s-tohntom haꞌichu wua aꞌai e wehm.
\c 10
\s1 Mash hema g anghil an uꞌukch g holiwk oꞌohana
\p 
\v 1 Ntki hahawa ab nei matki ab hema i hud g s-gewk anghil ab dahm kahchim amjed. Id oki g chewagikaj e enigadadch ch g kiohod an hab juhkch e-moꞌo an. Kuki g wuhioshaj hab mahs mo g tash. K g kakhioj hab mahs mo g mehi am wuhshanim.
\v 2 Id oki g s-apko e-tadkaj am keishch g ge shuhdagi ch g s-ohgig e-tadkaj am keishch g jewed. Kuki an hab chuꞌig g oꞌohana nowij ed ch pi holiwkas.
\v 3 Kuki am si s-kaidam neok ch hab sha kaidag mo g mawid ab todk. Kutki g wewaꞌak tataniki ab hahawa uhpam neneo todkch.
\v 4 Nt am haha wabsh wo i chum oꞌoha. Tki wabshaba ab hema neo dahm kahchim t amjed k hab kaij, “Pi g am hedai shaꞌi ahgid mo has kaij idam wewaꞌak tataniki. Pi g an hu shaꞌi oꞌohan.”
\p 
\v 5 Kutki ihda anghil mo an dahm kehk g ge kahchki ch jewed ab si uhgk i bei g s-apkojed e-nowi ab dahm kahchim wui
\v 6 k hab kaij, “Jiosh o chum hekid an haꞌichug ch nahto g dahm kahchim ch jewed kahchim ch ge kahchki ch wehs haꞌichu mo am ha eda idam k hab kaij mat am wa e ai mat geꞌe haꞌichu hab wo e juh.
\v 7 Wewaꞌakkokam anghil at am wo kuhu g e-kuikudkaj. T am hab haha wo juh g Jiosh g s-aꞌagi e-apchuda mo wa am ha ahgid hegam e-pionagbad mo d Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam.”
\p 
\v 8 Kutki hegai mo wa ab neok ni-wui ab dahm kahchim t amjed ab ep neok k hab kaij, “Neh, an o uꞌukch g oꞌohana hegai anghil mo an dahm kehk g kahchki ch jewed. Am g hihm k ab behꞌi.”
\p 
\v 9 Nt am hih wui hegai anghil k ab tahni mat wo ni-mah.
\p K hab kaij ab ni-wui, “Ab g be k huhgi. T wo si s-iꞌowik mapt wo huh ch wabshaba wo siwa am m-wohk ed.”
\v 10 Nt ab bei g al oꞌohana nowij ab k huh. K s-wohom si s-iꞌowi mant huh. Nt wabshaba am i bah. T hahawa si siwa am ni-wohk ed.
\p 
\v 11 Kum ab hahawa ep ni-ahgid ihda, “Am apt ep wo oꞌoha g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga ab ha amjed muꞌi nahnko mahs mehk jewed dakam hemajkam ch kokownal ch nahnko kaidam neneokdam.”
\c 11
\s1 Matsh gohk an wo i wuwhag k wo si s-mahch k ah haꞌichu
\p 
\v 1 Kumtki ab hahawa hema ni-mah g kuintakud uhs k hab ni-ahg, “I g wuhshani k an kuint g Jiosh cheopiga ch g iagchulidakud k wo ha kuint hegam mo am e hoꞌigeꞌidahun Jiosh wui amai.
\v 2 T wabshaba hegai mo an wehgaj kolhaitas am i e dagito ha wui g nahnko mahs hemajkam. Pt pi an hu has wo i juh. Idam nahnko mahs hemajkam at wo kehiwia hegai mo d chum si Hekia S-apꞌekam Kihhim am oidam g giꞌikko wehst-mahm gamai gohk (42) mashad.
\v 3 Jiosh o hab kaij, “Gohk ant wo ha mah g ni-pionag g gewkdag. T idam am wo ahgahi g haꞌichu ni-ahga ab wabsh shoꞌig e enigadad g dahumkaj heg oidam hemako mihl gohk siant chuhdpo wehst-mahm (1260) tash.”
\p 
\v 4 Neh, t am hahawa ni-chehgi matki has wo masmak idam gohk. Kutki hab wo masmak mo hegam gohk olive uꞌus wuhshanig mo wa heki hu oꞌohanas ab ha amjed ch hab ep wo masmak mo hegam gohk lalampa mo am chuhch geꞌe cheopi ch ed.
\v 5 Kuki g mehi ab i wushke ha-chihchini amjed ch ha kokda g ha-obga. Kut hedai wo i chum s-koꞌokam has ha juh k wo e kokda.
\v 6 Ab oki mahks g apꞌedag mat wo kuh g dahm kahchim. T pi wo ha juhkad heg oidam mat am wo ahgad g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga. Ab oki ep mahks g apꞌedag mat wo ehꞌedch g shohshonkam shuhdagi k an wo i wuhshad g nahnko mahs si shoꞌigdag ch mumkidag ia jewed dahm.
\p 
\v 7 Tki am wo i nahto g e-chikpan. Tki ab hema wo i wuhsh g s-ta ehbidamakam oꞌodham ge shuhdagi t amjed k e wepogidch g mischini haꞌichu doakam ch wo ha cheggia k wo ha gewito k wo ha kokda idam gohk.
\v 8 Tki g ha-koꞌidag am wo wehchkad wohg ch ed heg eda geꞌe kihhim mat wa amai g s-apꞌekam t-kownalig ab e naggia kots t ab. Ihda kihhim at e wepodad g si pi apꞌekam k hab e aꞌaga Sodom ch hab ep e aꞌaga Egypt.
\v 9 Wehs nahnko kaidam neneokdam an wehs jewed dahm atki wo ha neidad mat idam gohk am wo wehchk waik eda hugkam tash. Kumtki pi wo ha hiwigi mamt ged hu wo ha hihash.
\v 10 Tki g hemajkam wo si s-hehgigk mat koi ch wo pipiast k ab aꞌai wo e mah g haꞌichu mahkigdag noki pi ha shoꞌigchud idam gohk.
\p 
\v 11 Am i dahm g waik eda hugkam tash, ni am neid matki g Jiosh ab haha wo i ha mah g doakag. Tki wo gegokiwua. Kutki wehsijj hegam mat wo nei ihda wo si s-ehbeni.
\v 12 Kutki idam gohk wo kah mo ab hema si neok ab dahm kahchim t amjed ch hab kaij, “Ab g wo i hihim.” Kutki am wo i chehchsh dahm kahchim wui am chewagi ch ed am ha-neidag ed g e-obga.
\p 
\v 13 Tki am waꞌi hekaj am si s-gewkam wo uꞌugij g jewed. Kutki g hemako tahpani mo wehst-mahm e tahpanch (1/10) g kihhim wo i gei. Kutki wewaꞌak mihl (7000) hemajkam wo e koꞌij heg eda jewed uꞌugij. Kutki hegam haꞌi matki am wo wih wo shaꞌi si s-ehbeni k ab wo si has el g gewkdaj g Jiosh.
\p 
\v 14 Id o d i gokkokam haꞌichu s-ta ehbidamakam mat iaꞌi kuhgi. T wabshaba g waikkokam hahawa s-hohtam hab wo e juh.
\s1 Wewaꞌakkokam kuikud
\p 
\v 15 Kut g wewaꞌakkokam anghil am hahawa kuhu g e-kuikudkaj. K am haꞌi si s-kaidam neneok ab dahm kahchim t amjed ch hab kaij, “Wehs g kokownaltalig ia jewed dahm at d haha wo Jiosh kownaltaligk. Kut am wo ha dahmkad g si e-kehsha wehm iꞌajed ch chum hekid.”
\v 16 Kutki hegam gokko gamai giꞌik geꞌeged ab i shulig k gd hu si kokawua k ab ihm g Jiosh
\v 17 ch hab kaij:
\q1 “T-kownalig Jiosh, chum ap hekid an haꞌichug ch am hahawa wehs i chehgi g e-gewkdag k am i himch g e-kownaltalig.
\q1 Kuch heg hekaj ab si m-hoꞌigeꞌelid.
\q1 
\v 18 Hegam mo pi m-mahch o si s-babga.
\q1 Kut e ai mapt wo ha lodai.
\q1 Wehsijj g koꞌi at wo i wuwhag k wo e lodaitach.
\q1 Kupt wo ha mah g ha-mahkigdag g haꞌichu i m-tashogiddam ch wehs hegam mo d m-hemajkamga ch ab s-m-wohog elid, chum as hedai d wo k.
\q1 E at ai mapt gam hu hab wo i ha juh hegam mo padchud g jewed”
\m Neh, bo kaij hegam geꞌeged.
\p 
\v 19 Kutki g Jiosh cheopi an dahm kahchim ch ed ab i e kuhpiꞌo. T am e chehgi hegai uhs washa mo am eda wehch g Jiosh haꞌichu ahꞌadadag. Kut am si tohonno g wepgi. K an kaidag g tataniki. T g jewed uꞌugij. T g chea s-gewkam gei.
\c 12
\s1 Matsh hema g s-ta ehbidamakam wo ha shoꞌigch g Tutuligo
\p 
\v 1 Am atki hahawa haꞌichu si geꞌe e chehgi an dahm kahchim ch ed. Am aniki neid mat g uwi am hema i wuhsh. Kuki g ipudaj hab mahs mo g tash. Ihda uwi oki an keishch g mashad ch g gihko ab wahkch e-moꞌo ab. K id ab gamai gohk huhuꞌu an dadha.
\v 2 Kutki wo ge madt. Tki ab i hihhi g s-koꞌok matki wo mahmadho. K hekaj am si shoshshak.
\p 
\v 3 Am atki hahawa haꞌichu ep i e chehgi dahm kahchim ch ed. Niki am neid matki am hema i wuhshani k e wepogid g geꞌe nehbig hujud ch ge s-wegi ch ge wewaꞌak mohmi ch wehst-mahm aꞌag. K g gigiko an hab chuhchuꞌig wehs ha ab g mohmij.
\v 4 Kutki g e-baikaj i ha chewaim g hemako tahpani mo waik e tahpanch g huhuꞌu k im hu hab i ha juh ab dahm kahchim amjed ch am ha nehnich jewed dahm. Kutki wo mahmadho hegai uwi. T ihda Nehbig Hujud e wepogiddam am wui i kekiwua mat wo huh g madaj mat wabsh wo chum mahsi.
\v 5 Kutki am i mahmadho g uwi. Tsh g madaj am d wo kownalk wehs ha dahm g jejewed. Mtki am ha hekaj bei g ali k gam hu i bei Jiosh wui. K heg an da kownal daikud ed.
\v 6 Tki hegai uwi gam hu heb hu meh am tohono jewed ch ed. Am atki i apch g Jiosh wehhejed mat am wo e nuhkud hemako mihl gohk siant chuhdpo wehst-mahm (1260) tash.
\p 
\v 7-8 Tki an haha wabsh g cheggiadag hab e juh Jiosh kihdag ed. Hegai anghil mo hab chehgig Michael g e-anghiliga ha wehm oki cheggia g Nehbig Hujud. K wehs g jijawul am i wehmt g Nehbig Hujud. Tki wabshaba hegam Michael ha gehg. Kumtki hahawa pi ha hiwigi mas an ep wo haꞌichugk Jiosh kihdag ed.
\v 9 Ihda Nehbig Hujud atki gam hu si e wua ab amjed g dahm kahchim. Heg oki wud mash wa koꞌoi masma ch hab chehgig ge Jiawul ch hab ep chehgig Satan. Id o ha iattogid g wehs hemajkam an jewed dahm. Ab amt i ha nehnich g piongaj wehmaj.
\p 
\v 10 Ntki hahawa hema ep kah an dahm kahchim ch ed. Kuki id si s-kaidam hab kaij, “Neh, chum o hekid ab kehk g ge Jiawul Jiosh baꞌich ch ab chum haꞌichu ha abchud g Jiosh hemajkamga. T wabshaba g Jiosh gam hu i wuhshad k am i maskogi g si e-Kehsha gewkdag. Kut hab wa masma i e maskogi g ha-doꞌibiadag g Jiosh hemajkamga.
\p 
\v 11 “Jiosh si Kehsha at am i e dagito mat g ehꞌedaj e iagchul ab Jiosh wui. K g hemajkamgaj heg hekaj ab si hiwig ch s-ap ahgachug g wohokam ab amjed ch hab gehg g Jiawul, chum as hems wo e muhkid.
\v 12 T wo si s-hehgigk wehsijj hegam mo am haꞌichug Jiosh kihdag ed. T wabshaba wo si e shoꞌigch hegam mo am haꞌichug jewed dahm. Jiawul at si s-bagam ab wo i hud jewed dahm s-mahchch mo pi shaꞌi tash hiwgidas.”
\p 
\v 13 Pegih, am amtki wa daꞌich jewed dahm ihda Nehbig Hujud mo d Jiawul. Tki wa eda heki hu madt hegai uwi. T g Nehbig Hujud an ha hekaj i huꞌui.
\v 14 Kumtki ab aꞌanch g uwi g baꞌag aꞌankaj mat gam hu wo daꞌa k gan hu wo e ehstokch tohono jewed ch ed. Kumtki am wo nuhkudad waik eda hugkam aꞌahidag mat g Nehbig Hujud pi wo mua.
\v 15 Tki g Nehbig Hujud ab haha wabsh i iawua g shuhdagi e-chini amjed am oidk hegai uwi mat gam hu wo i chum moht.
\v 16 Tki wabshaba g jewed ab i wehmt g uwi, heg wa wepo mat ab i kuhpiꞌo g e-chini k im hu bah hegai shuhdagi mo ab daꞌiwuni Nehbig Hujud chini amjed.
\v 17 Tki haha wabsh wohoꞌi bagat g Nehbig Hujud ab wui g uwi k amjed am i ha cheggia hegam mo ab d amjedkamaj. Uwi amjedkam oki d hegam mo ab s-wohog elid g Jiosh chehanig ch ab s-wohochud hegai wohokam mat am i ha tashogi g Jesus.
\v 18 Kuki am hahawa kehk g Nehbig Hujud ge shuhdagi koa an.
\c 13
\s1 Matsh am wo i wuwha g gohk s-ta ehbidamakam oꞌodham
\p 
\v 1 Ntki haha wabsh nei hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam oꞌodham mo e wepogidch g mischini haꞌichu doakam. Id at ab i wuhsh ge shuhdagi t amjed k ge wehst-mahm aꞌag ch wewaꞌak mohmi. K an aꞌagaj an gigiko an shahshꞌai. K an mohmij an oꞌohadag g si pi apꞌekam chechgig.
\v 2 Ihda s-ta Ehbidamakam oki hab sha mahs mo g ohshod. K g tahtdaj hab sha mams mo g judumi tahtad. K g chinij hab mahs mo g mawid chini. T g Nehbig Hujud ab mah g gewkdag ch e-kownaltalig wehs jewed dahm.
\v 3 Hema g moꞌoj o hab sha mahs matki wa e muhkid k wabshaba ep doa k e chegito. Kut ab si has i el g hemajkam wehsko k am i oi ihda s-ta Ehbidamakam. T wehs hemajkam ab i ihm g Nehbig Hujud nat pi ab mah g e-gewkdag hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam
\v 4 k ab ep ihm g s-ta Ehbidamakam ch hab kaij, “Pi oki hedai hab shaꞌi masma mo ihda. Pi atki hedai wo shaꞌi e nako mat wo cheggia.”
\p 
\v 5 Kum wabsh hiwgid ihda mat wo si pi kehg neokad. Kumtki ab ep mah g gewkdag am oidam g giꞌikko wehst-mahm gamai gohk (42) mashad.
\v 6 Kut ihda am ha hekaj pad neo ab wui g Jiosh k pi ap hekaj g chehgigaj ch nahnko ahg g Jiosh kihdag ch hegam mo an kih kihdaj ed.
\v 7 Ab amtki hiwigi mat wo ha cheggia g Jiosh hemajkamga k wo ha gewito. Kumt ab ep mah g gewkdag am ha dahm g wehsko dakam hemajkam mo has i kaidam d neneokdam.
\v 8 K wabshaba g Jiosh hemajkamga ha chechgig o an oꞌohadag e doꞌibiakam ha-oꞌohana ed. Ihda oꞌohana o d enigaj hegai mat kahwalkaj e muhkid am ha wehhejed. Idam e doꞌibiakam at pi ab hu wo ihm hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam. Hegam waꞌi mo pi an hu oꞌohadag heg eda oꞌohana at ab wo ihmad hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam.
\p 
\v 9 Am g wo s-ap i aꞌamichud ihda.
\v 10 Hegam mo hedai d ha wuikam mat wo e kuhpach at hemho wa wo e kuhpach. Hegam mo d ha wuikam mat wo e koꞌij at hemho wa wo e koꞌij. K eda d ha-wuikam g Jiosh hemajkamga mat wo s-chu nakogad ch wo s-gewkk am e-wohochudadag ed.
\p 
\v 11 Ni hahawa ep neid matki ab hema ep i wuhsh ged hu jewed wecho amjed. Id o hab waꞌap mahs mo g s-ta ehbidamakam haꞌichu doakam ch ge gohk aꞌag hab sha masma mo g kahwal aꞌag ch hab masma neok mo g nehbig hujud.
\v 12 Hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam mat wehpeg i wuhsh oki ab mahkch g gewkdag hegai mat am hahawa i wuhsh. K heg ab wehs ha chehani g hemajkam jewed dahm mat ab wo si has elidad hegai wehpeg s-ta Ehbidamakam matki uhpam e chegito.
\v 13-14 K id hiwgid mat am hab juh g si geꞌe s-hasig haꞌichu. K wehs hemajkam neid mat ab i huduni g mehi dahm kahchim t amjed in jewed dahm. Bo wa masma wehs ha iattogid g hemajkam id dahm jewed ch d s-chu Iattomakam Haꞌichu i Tashogiddam ch ab ha chehani mat am haꞌichu wo nahto mat heg wo wepogidask s-ta Ehbidamakam mat wehpeg i wuhshani k atki e muhkid g is-pahyokaj k uhpam e chegito.
\v 15 Hegai s-chu Iattomakam Haꞌichu i Tashogiddam atki am ihbheiwua id eda mat am e nahto. Tki heg hekaj e nako ihda haꞌichu ha-nahtoi mat wo neok k ep wo ha kokda wehs hegam mat pi ab hu wo i shul wui.
\v 16 Tki ihda s-chu Iattomakam Haꞌichu i Tashogiddam i ha huilisamad wehs hemajkam matp hedai d wo i k mat an wo e chepos heg hekaj wehpeg s-ta Ehbidamakam cheposig. Kumtki wa woho an ge ha chechpos an s-apkojed ha-nohnhoi an ch ab ha-koka ab.
\v 17 Pi atki hedai wo e nako mas haꞌichu wo ha nolawt o haꞌichu wo gagda, heg hi wa mat ab wo cheposigk g s-ta Ehbidamakam chehgigkaj o heg hekaj nuhmilo mo d chehgigaj nuhmilo.
\p 
\v 18 Id oki d si s-juhk haꞌichu. Kut am wo i mamche matp hedai wo s-chu amichudad mo has d ahga hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam nuhmilo no pi hegai nuhmilo d chehgigaj hema oꞌodham. K ihda nuhmilo d chuhdp siant chuhdpo gamai chuhdp (666).
\c 14
\s1 E-doꞌibiakam ha-neꞌi
\p 
\v 1 Ntki ab ep nei Kuki hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch an kehk Sion doꞌag t ab. K id wehm g siant giꞌikko gamai giꞌik mihl (144,000) hemajkam am gegok. K an ha-koka an oꞌohadag g chehgigaj hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch ch heg ohg chehgig.
\v 2 Kuni kah mo ab hema neok dahm kahchim t amjed ch hab kaidag mo g geꞌe shuhdagi s-kaidam med ch hab kaidag mo g tataniki an doahim. Hegai mani kah o hab kaidag mo muꞌi aꞌalpa am e gew.
\v 3 Hegam hemajkam mani wa ha neid oki am ahg g wechij neꞌi ch am gegok wui hegai kownal daikud ch hegam ha wui giꞌik haꞌichu doakam ch hegam geꞌeged. Kutki pi hedai ep wo e nako mas wo mai g ha-nei.
\v 4 Idam oki d hegam mat pi shaꞌi ha hohont k si e nuhkud mo pi ha wehm wohppo. Kut am ha wehhejed e muhkid hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch k ha doꞌibia. Kuki idam an oidahim mo hebai i oimmed ch d wehpegkam e doꞌibiakam.
\v 5 Pi oki hekid haꞌichu ha iattogid ch pi ha chuꞌijig.
\s1 Mash haschu am ha ahgid g waik anghil
\p 
\v 6 Ntki hahawa hema ep nei g anghil. K id an daꞌa uhgk ch ahgahim g pi ha huhugedam s-kehg haꞌichu ahgaj g Jiosh ab ha wui g nahnko kaidam neneokdam an wehsko jewed dahm.
\v 7 Si o s-kaidam hab kaij, “Ab g wo si has elid g Jiosh ch ab ihm. E at ai mat wo ha lodai g hemajkam. Ab g wo i tohtonwua k ab wo i ihm g Jiosh. Heg at nahto g dahm kahchim ch jewed ch ge shuhdagi ch g shohshonkam shuhdagi.”
\p 
\v 8 Tki am hahawa hema ep i oi hegai wehpeg anghil k hab kaij, “I at gei ihda geꞌe kihhim. Wehs hemajkam o am hab wua g pi apꞌekam aꞌai e wehm id hekaj kihhim. K heg hekaj hab e aꞌaga Babylon. Shahag wepo mo ha nawkkoichud.” Neh, bo kaij hegai gokkokam anghil.
\p 
\v 9-10 Tki g waikkokam anghil am i ha oi hegam gohk k si s-kaidam hab kaij, “T wo ha mah g Jiosh g s-koꞌok namkidadag wehs hegam mo hedai ab si has elid hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam ch ab chechposidas heg hekaj cheposigaj e-koka ab o an e-nohnhoi an. Id o heg wa wepogidas mat g Jiosh ab wo ha mah g s-koꞌok nawait nat pi am wo s-koꞌokam ha mehi g haꞌichu s-mehidagkaj am ha tahgio g s-apꞌekam anghil ch hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch.
\v 11 T g kuhbdaj hegai mehi mat s-koꞌokam wo ha mehi am wo wuhshanid uhgk iaꞌi amjed ch chum hekid. Pi o am hu haꞌichug g ulinihogig ha wehhejed hegam mat ab i shul wui g s-ta Ehbidamakam ch ab wui g wepogidaj k ab e chepos heg hekaj chehgigaj.” Neh, bo kaij ihda anghil.
\p 
\v 12 Id att hekaj hemho wo wa si s-chu nakogad ahchim mach d Jiosh hemajkamga ch ab s-wohog elid g Jiosh chehanig ch am s-gewkam oid g Jesus.
\p 
\v 13 Ni hahawa hema ep kah. Kuki id ab neok dahm kahchim t amjed ch hab kaij mantsh an wo oꞌoha ihda, “T wo si s-ap e taht hegam mat wo koi, ab s-wohochudch mo g Jesus d ha-kownalig.”
\p K g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag hab kaij, “Do si wohokam ihda. T wo si s-ap e ulinihogi idam heg amjed s-wehch e-chikpan k ab wo bei g e-mahkigdag heg wehhejed.”
\s1 Matsh has wo chuꞌigk g geꞌe lodaita tash
\p 
\v 14 Ntki hahawa nei g s-toa chewagi. Kuki an id dahm hema dak ch hab mahs mo g Jiosh si Kehsha. K g ohla gihko ab e wahkch moꞌoj ab. K an uꞌukch g s-muꞌuk ohso.
\v 15 T ab hema i wuhsh g anghil ab amjed g geꞌe cheopi k ab si s-kaidam neok ch hab kaij heg wui mo an da chewagi ch ed, “Heg o wa wepogidas mapt an wo hikkumia g uhdwis bahidag g e-ohsokaj am wehsko jewed dahm. E at ai g geꞌe lodaita tash. Kupt am wo i ha hemapai g hemajkam heg wehhejed.”
\v 16 Kut hegai mo an da chewagi dahm ab si i widu g e-ohso an jewed dahm heg wa wepo mat am hab wo juh g oda.
\p 
\v 17 Niki hahawa hema ep neid g anghil. T heg ab i wuhsh cheopi t amjed an dahm kahchim ch ed k an hab waꞌap hema uꞌukch g s-muꞌuk ohso.
\p 
\v 18 K am hema ep kehk g anghil ch am nuhkud g nahda ab ab g iagchulidakud. Id at am hih heg wui mo g s-muꞌuk ohso an uꞌukch k si s-kaidam hab kaij, “E at ai g geꞌe lodaita tash. K heg wepogidas mapt an wo hikkumia g uhdwis g e-ohsokaj.”
\p 
\v 19 Kut wa woho ab i widu g anghil g e-ohso an jewed dahm k am hikkumia g uhdwis k am ha shul kehiwinakud ch ed. Id o am chehgidch mat g Jiosh s-koꞌokam wo ha namkid.
\v 20 Kum ha kehiwia g uhdwis gam hu jeg ed ab amjed g kihhim. T g ha-ehꞌed ab i meh ab amjed g kehiwinakud hab masma mo g wiꞌindag mo gohk siant mihya chewaj ch hetasp tad s-juhk.
\c 15
\s1 Hegam anghil matsh wo uꞌapa g si oidchkam shoꞌigdag
\p 
\v 1 Ntki hahawa ep nei g si geꞌe chehgida an dahm kahchim ch ed. Wewaꞌak anghil oki uꞌa g wewaꞌak shoꞌigdag. Idam oki d si ha oidchkam shoꞌigdag. Jiosh atki id hekaj am wo i kuhgi g s-gewk e-aꞌappemadag.
\p 
\v 2 Neid ani mo am haꞌichu tadani ch hab sha mahs mo g mi-lihda ch g mehi wehnags. Ha ani ep neid hegam mat gewito hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam pi ab hu has elidch g wepogidaj ch ab hu cheposig heg hekaj chehgigaj ch nuhmilo. Am oki gegok hugidaj an ihda mo sha mi-lihda mahs ch g aꞌalpa an uꞌukch mat g Jiosh ab ha mah.
\v 3 Mosesbad ch hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch oki ab ha mahkch g neꞌi. K id am aꞌaga:
\q1 “T-kownalig Jiosh, dap si s-gewkdagkam.
\q1 K g haꞌichu hab m-juni d si geꞌe haꞌichu ch shaꞌi si s-kehgaj.
\q1 T-kownalig an wehsko jewed dahm, do si s-apꞌekam ch wohokam g m-himdag.
\q1 
\v 4 Wehsijj att ab wo si has i m-el.
\q1 Pi at hedai wo shaꞌi pi am hu ah map d si haꞌichu nap pi ahpi d si hekia s-apꞌekam.
\q1 Wehs nahnko mahs hemajkam at ab wo i hihim k ab wo i shul m-wui no pi wehsijj neid g si s-apꞌekam haꞌichu hab m-juni.”
\p 
\v 5 Am i dahm ani hahawa ep neid moki ab kuhpiꞌokas g Jiosh cheopiga an dahm kahchim ch ed. Kuki heg eda am haꞌichug hegai ikus kih mo hab d ahga mo g Jiosh am ha wehmaj g e-hemajkamga.
\v 6 Tki ab i wuwha g wewaꞌak anghil k uꞌa g wewaꞌak si oidchkam shoꞌigdag ab amjed g cheopi. Idam anghil oki si s-kehg s-tohtam e enigadadch ch g ohla babshodag an hab juhkch e-babsho an.
\v 7 Tki hema hegam giꞌik haꞌichu doakam ab ha mah idam wewaꞌak anghil g wewaꞌak ohla hohas-hahaꞌa. Kuki idam shuhshudch g s-koꞌok namkidadag.
\v 8 Hegai cheopi o ab wabsh i shuhdags g kuhbskaj no pi am haꞌichug g s-tondam gewkdaj g Jiosh. Kut pi hedai wo e nako mas an hu wo i wah cheopi ch ed am hugkam mat wo kuhgi idam wewaꞌak shoꞌigdag mat uꞌapa hegam wewaꞌak anghil.
\c 16
\s1 Hohas-hahaꞌa mo shuhdags g Jiosh aꞌappemadag
\p 
\v 1 Kuni wa hema ep kah. K id am s-kaidam neok ab amjed g cheopi ab ha wui idam wewaꞌak anghil ch hab kaij, “Am g wo hihim k wo iawua g s-koꞌok namkidadag an jewed dahm ab ha amjed hegam hohas-hahaꞌa.”
\p 
\v 2 Tki g wehpegkam anghil am him k am iawua an dahm g jewed hegai mo wasibch e-hoas-haꞌa ch ed. Kutki g si s-koꞌok ch s-ta ehbidama hihiwdag ha ai hegam mo ab ha ab hab chuꞌig g s-ta Ehbidamakam cheposig ch idam mat i shul ab wui g wepogidaj.
\p 
\v 3 Tki amjed g gokkokam anghil am hahawa epai iawua hegai mo wasibch an ge shuhdagi dahm. Tki g shuhdagi hab masma e ehꞌedch mo g muhki ehꞌed. Tki wehs haꞌichu koi am ge shuhdagi ch ed.
\p 
\v 4 Tki amjed g waikkokam anghil am epai iawua hegai mo wasibch an aꞌakimel ch ed ch shohshonkam shuhdagi ch ed. Kutki e ehꞌedch g shuhdagi.
\v 5 Kuni kah mo hab kaij ab Jiosh wui hegai anghil mo nuhkud g shuhdagi:
\q1 “Dap si hekia s-apꞌekam Jiosh ch chum hekid an haꞌichug.
\q1 K ab d ha-wuikam idam g s-koꞌok namkidadag.
\q1 
\v 6 Iawua at g ha-ehꞌed g m-hemajkamga ch hegam haꞌichu i m-tashogiddam.
\q1 Kupt heg hekaj g ehꞌed ab ha mah mat wo ih.
\q1 Id o wa si e gahgid idam.”
\p 
\v 7 Niki amjed hahawa hema ep kah. K id ab neok iagchulidakud amjed ch hab kaij, “T-kownalig Jiosh, dap si s-gewkdagkam. K g m-lodaita si woho ch si s-apꞌe.”
\p 
\v 8 Tki amjed g giꞌikkokam anghil am iawua hegai mo wasibch an tash t an. Kut ha mehi g hemajkam g e-s-tonikaj.
\v 9 T eda idam pi gam hu s-ohhod g pi ap e-chegitoi. Jiosh o ha hiwgid mat wo e shoꞌigch. K heg hekaj ab si s-koꞌokam has ahg ch pi ab hu has elid g gewkdaj.
\p 
\v 10 Tki amjed g hetaspokam anghil am iawua hegai mo wasibch an dahm g s-ta Ehbidamakam kownal daikud. Kutki g s-chuhugam an gei wehsko s-ta Ehbidamakam kownalitalig ed. Kuki g hemajkam si e kihkꞌishch pi nakogch g s-koꞌok
\v 11 ch si pi kehg neneok ab Jiosh wui heg hekaj e-hihiwdag ch haꞌichu s-koꞌok ch wabshaba pi gam hu s-ohhod g pi ap e-chegitoi.
\p 
\v 12 Tki amjed g chuhdpokam anghil am iawua hegai mo wasibch heg eda ge akimel mo hab chehgig Euphrates. Tki gaksh ihda mat ab gahi wo i huhud g kokownal ab siꞌal wecho amjed.
\v 13 Niki hahawa ep neid g waik pi kehg gewpkdag. K idam hab mahs mo g babad ch d jijawul ch ab i wuwha ha-chihchini amjed g Nehbig Hujud ch g s-ta Ehbidamakam ch g s-chu Iattomkam Haꞌichu i Tashogiddam ch hab wua g s-hasig haꞌichu.
\v 14 Idam waik gewpkdag atki am hihi ha wui g kokownal an wehsko jewed dahm mat ab wo i ha hemapai. Kutki idam kokownal wo ha cheggia g Jiosh hemajkamga.
\p 
\v 15 (Bo kaij g Jiosh alidag, “Ab g wo ni-kaiham. Bant masma s-aꞌagi wo jiwia mo g s-chu ehskam. T wo s-ap e tahtkkad hegam mat wo s-nenenashanik. T wabshaba hegam mat pi hab wo masmak wo si e elidad hab sha masma mo an wabsh s-dahpkam oiopo.”)
\p 
\v 16 Tki amjed hegam waik gewpkdag am ha uꞌapa g kokownal amai mo g Tutuligo hab aꞌaga Armageddon.
\p 
\v 17 Tki amjed g wewaꞌakkokam anghil am iawua hegai mo wasibch an hewel ch ed. K ab hema si s-kaidam neok ab amjed hegai kownal daikud mo am da cheopi ch ed hab kaij, “Am at hab e juh.”
\v 18 Tki am si tohonno g wepgi k am si kokp g tataniki. Tki g jewed si s-gewkam uꞌugij. Pi oki hekid hab shaꞌi masma uꞌugij g jewed am i amjed mat an e nahto g oꞌodham. Id oki d si geꞌe jewed uꞌugij mo pi hebai hab shaꞌi masma.
\v 19 Tki hegai geꞌe kihhim waikpa e tahp. Kutki wehsko g kihhim gan hu aꞌai jewed dahm i shul. Jiosh o am wa s-chegitok hegai geꞌe kihhim mo hab e aꞌaga Babylon ch ab mah g s-koꞌok namkidadag. Id at heg wo wepogidask mat ab wo ih g si s-nawmdag nawait nat pi heg hekaj si s-koꞌokam wo e juh.
\v 20 Kutki wehs g siꞌiskod jejewed ch dohdaꞌag wo heb hu hihi.
\v 21 Tki g shaꞌi si geꞌeged chea an wo i shul. Idam oki hehemako am hu i siant s-wehch ch atki ab wo i shul dahm kahchim amjed am ha dahm hegam pi apꞌekam hemajkam. Kutki idam ab wo si pad neneo Jiosh wui.
\c 17
\s1 Hegai kihhim mo hab masma mo g si pi ap chehpaꞌawi uwi
\p 
\v 1 T amjed hegam hema wewaꞌak anghil mo an uhꞌukch g wewaꞌak hohas-hahaꞌa am jiwia ni-wui k hab kaij, “Ab g i hihm k neid ihda geꞌe kihhim mo am miabidch kehk g muꞌi aꞌakimel ch heg wepogidas mo g si pi apꞌekam chehpaꞌawi. Id at wehsko wo maꞌish g jewed g pi apꞌekamkaj.
\v 2 Kokownal wehsko jewed dahm at heg hekaj hab wo juh g pi apꞌekam. T g hemajkam wehsko jewed dahm wo noda hab juhkch g s-tohntom haꞌichu hab masma mamt wo nawkk iꞌok g nawait. Neh, nt am wo m-chehgi mat has masma ab wo bei g s-koꞌok e-namkidadag ihda pi apꞌekam kihhim.”
\p 
\v 3 T g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag ab si i ni-wehmt. Tki g anghil am i ni-bei tohono jewed wui. Ni am g uwi neid. Kuki id an daichug s-wegi s-ta ehbidamakam haꞌichu doakam ab. K id wewaꞌak mohmi ch wehst-mahm aꞌag. K g pi apꞌekam chechgig an oꞌohadag wehsko ab.
\v 4 Ihda uwi o si s-ihbhaimagim ch s-wegima e enigadadch ch g ohlakaj ch s-kehg hohodaikaj e hehosidch. K an nowij ed hab chuꞌig g ohla tahsa ch shuhdags g si s-uam haꞌichu. Id o hab d ahga mo d wabsh tohnto ihda kihhim.
\p 
\v 5 Ab koaj ab o oꞌohadag g chehgig. K id s-aꞌagi has d ahga ch hab chuꞌig, “Si Geꞌe Babylon kihhim o hab sha masma mo d ha-jeꞌe g wehs chechpaꞌawi ch totonto id dahm jewed.”
\v 6 Neid ani mat shaꞌi si s-ap e taht ihda uwi mat e koꞌij hegam mat pi dagito g Jesus. Heg o wa wepo mat nawm iꞌok g ha-ehꞌed.
\p Kunt am i neidok wabsh wohoꞌi si has ni-taht.
\p 
\v 7 K ab ni-kakke g anghil ch hab kaij, “Shahchu apt ahgk si has e taht. Am ant wo m-ahgi mo has d ahga ihda map s-neidma.
\v 8 Ihda s-ta Ehbidamakam mo wewaꞌak mohmi ch wehst-mahm aꞌag o d chum doakamkahim ch hahawa e muhkid k wabshaba ep wo e chegito k ab wo i wuhsh s-juhk wag t amjed k hahawa ep wo e muhkid. T heg hekaj wo si has i e taht g pi e doꞌibiakam. Idam o g ha-chechgig pi an hu oꞌohadag heg eda oꞌohana mo an g ha-chechgig oꞌohadag g e doꞌibiakam.
\p 
\v 9 “K d ha-wuikam g Jiosh hemajkamga mat wo s-amich ihda. Hegam wewaꞌak mohmi o d wewaꞌak kaꞌakwulk. K idam ha dahm daha ihda uwi. Idam mohmi o d ep wewaꞌak kokownal.
\v 10 Hetasp idam at im hu hab i e juh. K hemako d wabsh kia kownal. Kut hemako koi am hu i dahiwua k hekid am wo i dahiwua k pi shaꞌi tash am hu wo dakad.
\v 11 Hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam mat e muhkid at d wo gigiꞌikkokam kownalk. Id o ha wehm chikpan hegam wehpeg wewaꞌak kokownal ch gam hu wo him k wo e muhkid.
\p 
\v 12 “Hegam wehst-mahm aꞌag map neid o hab d ahga mat wehst-mahm kokownal ab ep wo i wuwha. Idam at heꞌes ab wo i wehmt hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam
\v 13 k ab wo mah g e-gewkdag no pi wehsijj e wepo masma haꞌichu hab elid.
\v 14 Idam at wo cheggia hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. T oi wa heg wo ha gewito no pi d geꞌe kownal am ha dahm g kokownal. T hegam mo si s-gewkam am oid ihda mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch am wehmaj wo ha gewito nat pi ab i ha waid k am i ha chuhcha.”
\p 
\v 15 K hab ep kaij g anghil ab ni-wui, “Am ap neid mo ihda uwi am muꞌi ha dahm daha g ge shuhshugi. K id hab d ahga mat g geꞌe pi apꞌekam kihhim am wo dahmkad muꞌi jejewed ch muꞌi nahnko mahs hemajkam.
\v 16-17 Kut g Jiosh hab wo ha juh hegam wehst-mahm kokownal mat ab wo wechokad g s-ta Ehbidamakam. Kut e wehm wo si s-kehꞌidad hegai geꞌe kihhim mo wepogidas g pi apꞌekam uwi ch wehs haꞌichu wo wohppoꞌi. T heg gam wabsh wo i dahpkad. T idam wo huh g chuhkugaj k wo hugio g meikaj. Neh, bat wa masma am oidk hab wo e juh mo has i kaij g Jiosh.
\v 18 Ihda uwi map neid o d hegai geꞌe kihhim mat s-gewkam an wo ha uꞌukch g kokownal aꞌai jewed dahm”
\c 18
\s1 Matsh wo i gei ihda geꞌe kihhim
\p 
\v 1 Am i dahm, ni hahawa ep neid g anghil. Tki id ab i hud dahm kahchim t amjed k geꞌe uꞌukch g gewkdag. K ab amjed g tonlig wabsh wehsko tonod an jewed dahm.
\v 2 K am si s-kaidam neok ch hab kaij:
\q1 “I at gei ihda geꞌe kihhim mo hab masma mo g chehpaꞌawi.
\q1 Jijawul o ebkiod.
\q1 Nahnko mahs s-uꞌamakam ch pi aꞌamkam uꞌuwhig o am kih eda.
\q1 
\v 3 Bat wa masma e padch g kihhim nat pi muꞌi ha padch g hemajkam g pi apꞌekamkaj.
\q1 Heg o wa wepo mat ha nawkkoich.
\q1 T am wehmaj ab wo bei g s-koꞌok namkidadag.
\q1 T g kokownal wehsko hab juh g pi apꞌekam id hekaj kihhim mo g chehpaꞌawi wepogidas.
\q1 T g s-kakais wehsko jewed dahm baꞌich i s-e kakaisch heg hekaj pi apꞌekam mo am hab e wua.”
\m Neh, bo kaij g anghil.
\p 
\v 4 Ni hahawa ep kah mo ab neok g Jiosh dahm kahchim amjed ch hab kaij:
\q1 “Ab g wo i wuwhaki, ni-hemajkamga.
\q1 Ab g wo i wuwhaki ab amjed ihda kihhim mo hab sha masma mo g chehpaꞌawi.
\q1 Pi g am hu wo wehmajk heg eda pi apꞌekam.
\q1 Pi g ab hu wo wehmaj behꞌi g s-koꞌok namkidadaj.
\q1 
\v 5 Pi ap chuꞌijigaj o shaꞌi si uhgk sipulkas.
\q1 Kuni s-chegito g pi ap chuꞌijigaj.
\q1 
\v 6 S-koꞌokam at hab em-juh.
\q1 Kumt uhpam s-koꞌokam hab wo juh.
\q1 Ab g baꞌich wo i nodgid g chuꞌijigaj wui.
\q1 Heg at wo wa wepodagk mamt am wo i shuhdad g kohbaj heg hekaj iꞌidag mo e dahm baꞌich i s-gewk mat wa has i masma am hab em-juh.
\q1 
\v 7 Ab g wo mahki g haꞌas shoꞌigdag ch pi ap tahhadkam mo wa heꞌes hejel ab e mahkch g ab si has e-elidadag ch kaisdag.
\q1 T wo si e shoꞌigch hab masma mo g hejel wiꞌikam uwi k eda hab e elid mo d kownal ch pi hekid wo e shoꞌigch.
\q1 
\v 8 Kut id hekaj g shoꞌigdaj wehs ab wo i shul dahm wabsh shel i e oidam.
\q1 K g shoꞌigdaj d s-koꞌok mumkidag ch pi ap tahhadkam ch bihugig Am at wo meitto ihda kihhim.
\q1 S-gewkdag ani ch wo lodait k s-koꞌokam wo namkid.”
\m Neh, bo kaij g Jiosh.
\p 
\v 9 Hegam kokownal mo wehmaj hab junihim g pi apꞌekam at wo si shoanid wehhejed am i neidok mamt mei.
\v 10 Idam o ga hu wabsh mehk gegok no pi s-ehbid mat wo nei g shoꞌigdaj ch hab kaij:
\q1 “Ih, shoꞌig! Ihda si geꞌe s-gewk kihhim mo e wepogid g Babylon at shaꞌi si s-hohtam ab bei g s-koꞌok e-namkidadag.”
\p 
\v 11 K g s-kakais id dahm jewed hab waꞌap si shoani ch pi ap e tahtk wehhejed no pi hahawa pi hedai ha nolawt g ha-gagli.
\v 12 Pi oki hedai ha nolawt g ha-ohlaga ch ha-plahdaga ch s-namkig hohodai ch g s-namkig ha-lohbaga ch g mamskal ch g s-namkig uhs. Nahnko haꞌichu oki hab wua g al-huandi aꞌagkaj ch s-namkig uhs ch kohwli ch wainomi k ch s-namkig hodaikaj. K oi wa pi hedai ha nolawt.
\v 13 Am o chum gagda hegai mo haschu am wehnads g haꞌichu hugi ch nahnko mahs s-ap uhwchu ch nawait ch e koꞌadam a-saidi ch chuꞌi ch pilkani ch haiwani ch kahwal ch kakawyu ch kakalit ch nenehol ch chum hems g oꞌodham dodakag. K pi hedai ha nolawt.
\p 
\v 14 K hab kaij idam s-kakais ab wui hegai kihhim:
\q1 “Wehs hegai map ab si tatchua at huhug.
\q1 M-kaisdag ch s-m-kehgdag at im hu hab i e juh.
\q1 Kupt pi dahm ep wo ha edagi.”
\p 
\v 15 Hegam mat s-e kakaisch am haꞌichu gagdak atki ga hu wabsh mehk wo gegokk no pi s-ehbid g shoꞌigdaj. Idam at wo si shoanid ch wo pi ap e tahtkkad
\v 16 ch hab wo kaijchid:
\q1 “Ih, shaꞌi si shoꞌig ihda si geꞌe kihhim mat wa eda ab wo si s-kehg e enigadadch g s-ihbhaimagi ch s-wegi lohbakaj k ab hab wo juhkchid g ohla hehosimhuna ch s-kehg hohodai.
\q1 
\v 17 T eda shaꞌi si s-hohtam wehs heb hu shul g e-kaisdag.”
\p Wehsijj oki ga hu wabsh mehk gegok hegam mo d ha-geꞌegeꞌejig an wapalko ch ed ch hegam mo an dadhaichug ch hegam mo d pion an wapalko ch ed ch wehs hegam mo ab behe g e-kihdag ab ge shuhdagi t amjed.
\v 18 Am o meihim g kihhim ch g kuhbs am wuhshani. K wehs idam am neid ch si hihnk ch hab kaij, “Pi o hekid hema kihhim hab shaꞌi masma d geꞌe kihhim.”
\v 19 T idam ab hahawa iawua g jewed e-moꞌo ab k si s-kaidam hihnk ch si shoani ch hab kaij:
\q1 “Shoꞌig, shoꞌig, ihda si geꞌe kihhim.
\q1 Ihda kihhim o wud mat ia s-e kakaisch hegam mo eꞌedgid g wapalko.
\q1 Shaꞌi si s-hohtam at wehs haꞌichu heb hu shul ihda kihhim.”
\m Neh, bo kaij idam pi apꞌekam hemajkam.
\p 
\v 20 Kut oi wa d wo si geꞌe s-hehgigk an dahm kahchim ch ed mat i gei ihda pi apꞌekam kihhim. Jesus chuhchai ch Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam ch wehs g Jiosh hemajkamga at wo si s-hehgigk. Jiosh at ab wo abch ihda kihhim g chuꞌijig mo has ha juhkchkahim.
\p 
\v 21 Kut am hahawa hema i e chehgi g si s-gewk anghil k am hema bei g hodai. Ihda hodai oki haꞌas geꞌej mo g si geꞌe chuꞌikud. T g anghil am daꞌich ge shuhdagi ch ed k hab kaij:
\q1 “Bat masma am wo si e daꞌich ihda geꞌe kihhim mat pi hekid hedai ep wo neidad.
\q1 
\v 22 Hegam mumsigo mo ha gew g aꞌalpa ch uhs kukuikud ch kohwli kukuikud at pi hekid am hu ep wo piast amai.
\q1 Pi at hekid am hu ep wo e chikp g nahnko mahs chikpan amai.
\q1 Pi amt hekid am hu wo chuꞌad.
\q1 
\v 23 Pi at hekid am hu ep wo e mehmheid g lalampa.
\q1 Pi at hekid hedai am hu ep wo e hohont.
\q1 Hegam mo d s-kakais iia o wa uꞌukch g gewkdag wehsko jewed dahm.
\q1 K wa ia ge has e wuihim g mamakai ch hekaj ha iattogid g hemajkam an wehs jewed dahm.
\q1 T eda wehs huhug ihda.”
\m Neh, bo kaij hegai anghil.
\p 
\v 24 Kumtki s-koꞌokam wo namkid g kihhim nat pi ia e koꞌij g Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam ch Jiosh hemajkamga. Chum o hems d chuꞌijigaj hegam mat gan hu aꞌai jewed dahm e koꞌij.
\c 19
\p 
\v 1 Nt amjed hahawa haꞌichu kah. K id hab kaidag mo shaꞌi muꞌi hemajkam am neneok an dahm kahchim ch ed ch hab kaij:
\q1 “Ab ach si has elid g Jiosh.
\q1 Doꞌibiadag ch ab has elidadag ch gewkdag o ab d amjedkamaj g Jiosh.
\q1 
\v 2 Do wohokam ch s-apꞌekam g Jiosh lodaita nat pi s-koꞌokam ab namkid ihda si pi apꞌekam chehpaꞌawi mo padchud g jewed heg hekaj e-tohntomdadag.
\q1 Jiosh at s-koꞌokam ab namkid nat pi ha kokda g piongaj.”
\m 
\v 3 K am ep Hihnk ch hab kaij:
\q1 “Ab ach si has elid g Jiosh.
\q1 Mei at ihda geꞌe pi apꞌekam kihhim.
\q1 T g kuhbs ab amjed chum hekid am wo wuhshanid.”
\p 
\v 4 K eda an dahm kahchim ch ed daha g Jiosh e-kownal daikud an. T ab wui i tohtonwua hegam gokko gamai giꞌik geꞌeged k ab si has elid ch hab kaij, “Pegih neh, ab ach si has elid g Jiosh.”
\s1 Matsh g Jiosh alidag am wo i ha hemapai g e-hemajkamga
\p 
\v 5 K ab hahawa hema neok miajed g Jiosh kownal daikud ch hab kaij:
\q1 “Ab g wo si has i elid g Jiosh ch ab s-wohog elid ahpim piongaj ch ahpim wehs hemajkam mam haꞌi d s-has hahaꞌichu ch haꞌi pi d has hahaꞌichu.”
\p 
\v 6 Ni hahawa ep kah muꞌi hemajkam. K g ha-neꞌoki hab kaidag mo g s-gewk shuhdagi an med ch hab kaidag mat g tataniki ab si s-kaidam kop. Ha ani kah mo hab kaij:
\q1 “Ab ach ihm g Jiosh no pi d si uhgk t-kownalig ch uꞌukch g gewkdag am wehs hemajkam ha dahm.
\q1 
\v 7 Ab att wo si i s-hehgigk ch wo s-ap t-tahtkkad ch ab wo si has i el g gewkdaj.
\q1 E at ai mat ab wo i ha hemapai g e-hemajkamga hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch.
\q1 T heg wo wa wepodagk mo g si geꞌe hohnta.
\q1 T g hemajkamgaj ab si e nahto wehhejed
\q1 
\v 8 hab sha masma mat g wo kuntam ab si s-tohama wo e enigadad.
\q1 Ihda lohba o wepogidas g s-apꞌekam haꞌichu hab ha-juni.”
\p 
\v 9 K hab kaij g anghil ab ni-wui, “An g oꞌohan ihda: Ab at wo i ha hemapai g e-hemajkamga hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. Kut wo si s-hehgigk hab masma mamt wo si s-hehgigk am ha-gegosig ed g wo ha hohntam.” K hab ep kaij g anghil, “Id o d si s-wohokam Jiosh neꞌoki.”
\v 10 Kunt am hahawa si i gei wecho k ab si has i el. K wabshaba hab kaij ab ni-wui, “Pi g hab masma ab si has ni-elid mani d Jiosh. Ab g si ihm g Jiosh. Dani wabsh piongaj hab masma mam ahpim mam ab s-wohochud hegai wohokam mat g Jesus am i em-tashogi.” Neh, bo kaij g anghil. K ihda wohokam d hegai mo ab amjed an uꞌukch g e-amichudadag g Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam.
\s1 Hegai mo g s-toa kawyu cheshajchug
\p 
\v 11 Nt hahawa ep nei g dahm kahchim. T i e kuhpiꞌo. K am hab chuꞌig g s-toa kawyu. K an ab da hegai mam hab aꞌaga Wohokam. Heg o d hegai mo am s-ap ha lodait ch s-ap hab wua g cheggiadag.
\v 12 Wuhpuij o hab masma s-mahs mo ab mehmheihim. K muꞌi gigiko an hab chuhchuꞌig moꞌoj an. An o hema oꞌohadag g chehgig ab ab. K heg waꞌi hejel s-mahch mo haschu wud.
\v 13 K g lihwaj d wabsh i ehꞌed. Kum hab aꞌaga Jiosh Neꞌoki no pi g Jiosh am gahi wuhshanim neok ab t-wui.
\v 14 T g muꞌi anghil am i oi hab masma mo g shondal k g s-tohta kakawyu ha chehchejch ch s-tohtam e eꞌenigadadch.
\v 15 Is-pahyo o ab i wuhshanis chinij amjed hegai Jiosh Neꞌoki. T id heg hekaj wo ha gewito g jejewed k am hahawa s-gewkam wo i ha wanim g wainomi usagakaj k s-koꞌokam wo ha namkid hegam mo bagachud g Jiosh. Id at heg wo wa wepodagk mamt g uhdwis wo kehiwia.
\v 16 Ab lihwaj ab ch an kahioj an o id chehgig an oꞌohadag ‘Si Geꞌe Kownal am Wehs ha Dahm g Kokownal.’
\p 
\v 17 Ni hahawa hema ep neid g anghil. Id o am kehk tash ch ed. K eda g uꞌuwhig an nenꞌe hewel ch ed. K id ab ha wui si s-kaidam neok ch hab kaij, “Am g wo hihim k am wo i e hemapai mat g Jiosh am hab wo em-juni g si geꞌe gegosig.
\v 18 T wo em-gegos g pi ap hemajkam ha-chuhkugkaj. Kumt chum hems wo huh g ha-chuhkug g kokownal ch shondal ha-geꞌegeꞌejig ch s-has hahaꞌichu ch ep wo huh g ha-chuhkug g kakawyu ch hegam mo ha chehchejch ch hegam mo d nenehol.”
\p 
\v 19 Ni hahawa ep neid hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam mat wa heki hu in i wuhsh. Wehs g kokownal an jewed dahm at am i ha hemapai g e-shondalig k am i wehmt g s-ta Ehbidamakam mat wo cheggia hegai mo g s-toa kawyu cheshaj. Kut id g shondaligaj i wehmt.
\v 20 Kumt bei hegai s-ta Ehbidamakam ch heg ehp s-chu Iattomkam Haꞌichu i Tashogiddam. Do ihda mo wa ha iattogid g s-hasig haꞌichukaj hegam mo ab hab juhkch g s-ta Ehbidamakam cheposig ch hegam mat ab i shul wui g wepogidaj. Kumt ha ui hegam gohk k wabsh doakk am ha nehnich heg eda kahchki mo chum hekid meihim.
\v 21 Hegai mo wa g s-toa kawyu cheshaj at ha kokda g ha-shondalig heg hekaj is-pahyo mo wa kamshch ab e-chini ed. Kut g uꞌuwhig am huh g ha-chuhkug k si s-kokwod.
\c 20
\s1 Hemako mihl aꞌahidag
\p 
\v 1 Ni amjed hahawa hema ep neid g anghil. T id ab i hud dahm kahchim amjed k an uꞌukch g yahwi id wehhejed s-juhk wag ch an uꞌukch g chew e hukshchim wainomi.
\v 2 K am daha g Nehbig Hujud ch d ge Jiawul ch hab chehgig Satan. Tki g anghil an si wulshp
\v 3 k am daꞌich heg eda s-juhk wag k ab si yahwidad k ab ep si bidsh. T hab pi ab hu ep wo i wuhshani k pi ep wo ha iattogi g hemajkam am hugkam mat wo e ai g hemako mihl aꞌahidag. Id at i dahm am hi wa ep wo shaꞌi e dagito pi shaꞌi tash.
\p 
\v 4 Kuni hahawa ep neid g kokownal dadaikud ch hegam mo an dadha. Idam amtki ab ha mah g gewkdag mat d wo uꞌusagakamk. Am ani ep ha neid hegam mat e koꞌij no pi am ahgachug hegai Jiosh haꞌichu ahga mo g Jesus am ha tashogid. Idam at pi ab hu shaꞌi has i el g s-ta Ehbidamakam niꞌis g cheposigajkaj ab hu e chechpos e-koka an o e-nohnhoi an. Jiosh at ab ha mah g apꞌedag mat ab wo i wuwha muhkig amjed k am wo i ha wanimedad g hemajkam wehmaj g Christ hemako mihl aꞌahid ab.
\v 5-6 Hegam mat wehpeg ab wo i wuwha muhkig amjed at wo si s-hehgigk ch wo si s-ap e tahtkkad ch pi am hu gahi ep wo wuwha g muhkig. Jiosh at hab wo ha juh mat d wo papalk ch d wo piongajk g alidag. Kut heg wehm am wo i ha wanim g hemajkam hemako mihl aꞌahid ab. (5) T wabshaba pi koi ab hu uhpam wo i e chechegito hegam mo pi mahch g Jiosh am hugkam mat wo huhug g hemako mihl aꞌahidag.
\s1 Mamtsh wo gewito g ge Jiawul
\p 
\v 7 Am i dahm g hemako mihl aꞌahidag, mtki ab wo i wuhshad g ge Jiawul amjed mam am kuhpch.
\v 8 Kutki am wo him k am ep wo ha iattogi g hemajkam an wehsko jewed dahm. Idam hemajkam at haꞌi hab wo e aꞌagad Gog Oꞌodham ch haꞌi hab wo e aꞌagad Magog Oꞌodham. Kut g Jiawul am wo i ha hemapai mat hab wo juh g cheggiadag. Kutki hab sha masma wo muꞌijk mo g oꞌod an shuhdagi bahsho
\v 9 ch am wehskojed wo i e hemapad k an wo e keshwua ha wehgaj hegam mo d Jiosh hemajkamga ch am kih Jerusalem ch ed. T oi wa g mehi ab wo i hud dahm kahchim t amjed k wo ha hugio.
\v 10 Mt amjed g ge Jiawul am daꞌich heg eda kahchki mo chum hekid meihim. Do ihda mei kahchki mamt am eda heki hu ha nehnich g s-ta Ehbidamakam ch s-chu Iattomkam Haꞌichu i Tashogiddam. Idam atki ab wo nako g s-koꞌok tash oidam ch chuhug oidam am i amjed ch chum hekid.
\s1 Si oidchkam lodaita
\p 
\v 11 Ni hahawa ep neid mo g si geꞌe s-toa kownal daikud am kehk. K ab daha g Jiosh. T g jewed ch dahm kahchim heb hu wohp ab amjed k pi hekid ep shaꞌi e neid.
\p 
\v 12 Kuni ha neid hegam mo d koꞌi ch d nahnko i mahs hemajkam. Idam o am gegok wui g kownal daikud. Kut i e kuhkpiꞌo hegam oꞌohana mo an oꞌohadag g pi ap ha-chuꞌijig. T am ep i e kuhpiꞌo hegai oꞌohana mo am eda oꞌohadag g e doꞌibiakam ha-chechgig. T g Jiosh ha lodai g koꞌi.
\v 13 Wehsijj at i wuwha ab ge shuhdagi t amjed ch ab hihaꞌini t amjed an wehsko jewed dahm. T g Jiosh ha lodai heg hekaj mo haschu i pi ap has junihim.
\v 14-15 Pi o an hu oꞌohanas g ha-chechgig heg eda oꞌohana mo an oꞌohanas g e doꞌibiakam ha-chechgig. Kumt hekaj am ha shul heg eda kahchki mo meihim. Id at hab wo masmak mo g gokkokam muhkig. T g Jiosh am wo hugio g muhkig k am ep wo hugio amai mo am haꞌichug g koꞌi.
\c 21
\s1 Matsh g Jiosh am hab hahawa ep wo juh g wechij dahm kahchim ch wechij jewed
\p 
\v 1 Ni hahawa ep neid g si wechij dahm kahchim ch si wechij jewed. Hegai wehpeg dahm kahchim ch wehpeg jewed at wa heb hu hihi. T g ge shuhdagi am wabsh i huhug.
\v 2 K ab i hudunihim g si Hekia S-apꞌekam Kihhim dahm kahchim t amjed. Id atki g Jiosh nahto. K hab e aꞌaga Wechij Jerusalem ch si e nahtokch am wehhejed g Jiosh alidag hab sha masma mat g wo kuntam wo si e nahtokch mat wo nam g wo e-kunta.
\p 
\v 3 Ab o daha g Jiosh e-kownal daikud ab. Kuni kah mo hab kaij, “Idani at g ni-kihdag ia i hud ha wui g hemajkam. Am ant ha wehm wo kihkad. Kut d wo ni-hemajkamgak. Am ant wo ha wehmajk ch d wo ha-Jioshgak
\v 4 ch ab wo i dagiꞌo g ha-ohꞌog ab ha-wuhpui ab. Pi at hedai haha wo muh o pi ap wo e tahtkkad o wo shoakad o wo tahtkkad g s-koꞌok. Im at hu hab i e juh g hekiukam.”
\p 
\v 5 Neh, bo kaij g Jiosh ch amjed hab ep kaij, “Idani ant am hahawa si wechij nahto wehs haꞌichu,” ch hab ep kaij ab ni-wui, “An g oꞌohan ihda wohokam mani m-ahgid. Wehs hemajkam at ab wo chum s-wohoch,”
\p 
\v 6 K hab ep kaij, “E at nahto wehs haꞌichu. Ahni ani d alpha ch d omega. Id o hab d ahga mani si wehpeg ia haꞌichug ch si ha oidch ia wabsh wo kia haꞌichugk. Nt wo ha mah g pi ha huhugedam doakag hegam matp hedai wo tatchua hab masma mamt wo ha wasibi g tonkkoi g shuhdagi.
\v 7 Ab ant ni-wui wo i ha gawulkai mat d wo ni-aꞌaligak hegam mat hedai i gewito g pi apꞌekam.
\v 8 T wabshaba wo e nehnich mei kahchki ch ed g s-chu ehbidkam ch pi wohochuddam ch hegam mo loligog ch chum e uꞌuwichud o chum e chechojchud ch ha muꞌadkam ch totonto ch s-chu hihoinkam ch s-chu iꞌattomkam ch hegam mo wabsh g oꞌodham nahtoi ha jijoshchud. Hegai mei kahchki o d gokkokam muhkig.”
\s1 Mash has mahs hegai wechij Jerusalem
\p 
\v 9 Hema hegam wewaꞌak anghil mat am uꞌapa g si oidchkam shoꞌigdag at am jiwia ni-wui k hab kaij, “Ab g i hihm. Nt am wo m-chehgi hegam mo d hohnigaj hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch.”
\v 10 T g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag ab si i ni-wehmt. T g anghil am i ni-be k am ni-uꞌapa si uhgk doꞌag dahm k ab i ni-chehgi hegai hekia s-apꞌekam kihhim mo d Wechij Jerusalem. Id o ab hudunihim dahm kahchim t amjed ch d Jiosh nahtoi
\v 11 ch si tonod g Jiosh tonligkaj hab masma mo hegai si s-kehg gai tondam hodai mo hab e aꞌaga jasper.
\v 12 An kihhim wehgaj o hab chuꞌig g uhgk kolhai. K id eda hab chuꞌig g gamai gohk kihkijeg. K g gamai gohk anghil ab ha nuhkud g kihkijeg. An o kihkijeg t an hab chuꞌig g ha-chechgig hegam gamai gohk dakam Tutuligo hemajkam.
\v 13 Waik kihkijeg o hab chuꞌig an siꞌalig tahgio ch waik an juhpin tahgio ch waik an wakolim tahgio ch waik an hudunig tahgio.
\v 14 K ihda kihhim kolhaidag o an hab junis gamai gohk hohodai dahm. K idam ha ab an oꞌohadag g ha-chechgig hegam gamai gohk chuhchaij hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch.
\p 
\v 15 Hegai anghil mo ab ni-wui neok o g ohla kuintakud uhs an uꞌukch mat hekaj wo kuint g kihhim ch g kolhaidaj ch g kihkijeg.
\v 16 K ihda kihhim si s-ap s-chuhchpul ch haꞌas uhgk ch haꞌas chewaj mo heꞌes i s-tadani. T g anghil am kuint. K d mihl hetasp siant (1500) mihya.
\v 17 T g anghil am ep kuint g kolhaidag. K d gohk siant gamai chuhdp (216) tad uhgk.
\v 18 K hegai kolhai heg hekaj hab junis hodai mo hab e aꞌaga jasper. K g kihhim d wabsh gai tondam ohla.
\v 19 K g shondaj id hekaj hab junis nahnko mahs si s-kehg hohodai. Wehpeg shondaj o d hegai hodai mo hab e aꞌaga jasper. K g gokkokam d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga sapphire. K g waikkokam d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga agate. K g giꞌikkokam d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga emerald.
\v 20 K g hetaspokam d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga onyx. K g chuhdpokam d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga carnelian. K g wewaꞌakkokam s-oam ch d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga quartz. K g gigiꞌikkokam d hegai mo ab e aꞌaga beryl. K g humuktokam d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga topaz. K g wehst-mahmhokam d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga chalcedony. K g gamai hemako d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga turquoise. K g gamai gokkokam d hegai mo hab e aꞌaga amedyst.
\v 21 K g gamai gohk kihkijeg d hegai hodai mo hab e aꞌaga pearl. Wehsijj hegam kihkijeg o hab junis ab hehemako pearl amjed. K g kahya am kihhim ch ed d wabsh ohla ch am wabsh gai tonod hab masma mo g mi-lihda.
\p 
\v 22 Pi ani shaꞌi hema neid g cheopi. Wehs g kihhim o d wabsh ge cheopi no pi an eda kihdag g Jiosh ch hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch.
\v 23 Pi o an hu haꞌichug g tash ch mashad. Jiosh o an wehsko tonlidch g kihhim heg wehm mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch g si geꞌe e-gewkdagkaj.
\v 24 Hemajkam am jewed dahm at s-ap am wo hihimad id hekaj tonlig. T g kokownal am wo uꞌapa g e-kakaisdag.
\v 25 T g kihkijeg chum hekid ab wabsh wo kuhkpiꞌokask. Pi at hekid wo s-chuchkagad. T heg hekaj pi ab hu wo i e kuhkp g kihkijeg.
\v 26 Si s-has hahaꞌichu am wehs jejewed ch ed at am wo uꞌapa g e-kakaisdag.
\v 27 T wabshaba pi am hu wo hiwgidask g s-uam haꞌichu. T pi ab hu wo i wahp g s-chu iꞌattomkam ch hegam mo hab junihim g s-ta edam haꞌichu. Hegam at am wo waꞌi wahpkad heg eda kihhim mo g ha-chechgig an oꞌohadag heg eda mo g e doꞌibiakam ha-chechgig an oꞌohadag. Id o d oꞌohanaj hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch.
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 T am hahawa ni-chehgi g akimel hegai anghil. K id ab daꞌiwuni heg amjed kownal daikud mo g Jiosh an daha heg wehm mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. K hab d ahga ihda mo g Jiosh ab t-mahkch g pi ha huhugedam doakag. Shuhdagi o si tohonnod hab masma mo g tondam hodai
\v 2 ch an si eda med g kahya. K g doakag uhs ge aꞌaijed shohshon ch an aꞌai kehk ihda akimel ch an babhe hemho wehs mashad ab. K g hahhagaj d ha-kulaniga g nahnko mahs hemajkam wehsko jewed dahm.
\v 3 K pi an hu haꞌichug hegai mo pi hohhoꞌidachud g Jiosh.
\p Am at wo haꞌichugk g Jiosh kownal daikud. Kut an wo dakad hegai mo kahwalkaj ab e chehgidch. T g piongaj ab wo si has elidad
\v 4 ch wo neidad g wuhioshaj. T g chehgigaj an wo oꞌohadagk ha-koka ab.
\v 5 Pi at dahm ep wo s-chuhugamk nat pi g tonlig aꞌai wo wuhshanid ab amjed g Jiosh. Kut pi an hu wo haꞌichugk g tash. T pi wo e tatchuad g lalampa. T g Jiosh hemajkamga am d wo kokownalk chum hekid.
\s1 Matsh ep wo jiwia g Jesus jewed dahm
\p 
\v 6 K hab hahawa ep kaij g anghil ab ni-wui, “Idam haꞌichu ahga o woho. Kut wehsijj ab wo chum s-wohoch. Jiosh o wa ab ha mahkch g haꞌichu i e-tashogiddam g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag mat am wo haꞌichu ha chehgi ch am ep ni-chehani mant am wo em-chehgi hegai mat haschu has wo e juh s-hohtam.” Neh, bo kaij g anghil.
\p 
\v 7 K g Jesus hab kaij, “Ab g wo i ni-kaiham. S-hohtam ant wo jiwia. Jiosh at wo wa s-ha hoꞌigeꞌel hegam mat ab wo s-wohog el wehs ihda gam hu baꞌich haꞌichu ahga mo in oꞌohanas.” Neh, bo kaij.
\p 
\v 8 Kuni ahni John wehs kah ch wehs neid ihda mani in oꞌohan id eda oꞌohana. Am o wa kehk hegai anghil mo ab ni-wui neok. Nt ab i gei wecho k ab chum si has elid am i neidok k kaiok ihda wehs.
\v 9 K wabshaba hab kaij ab ni-wui, “Pi g am hab e juhni. Dani wabsh em-wehm pion ahpim Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam ch wehs hegam mo ab s-wohog elid mo haschu an oꞌohadag id eda oꞌohana. Ab g has i elid g Jiosh.”
\p 
\v 10 K hab ep kaij ab ni-wui, “E o aihim mat wehs am hab wo e juh ihda map neid ch kah ch an oꞌohan. Pi g am ehsto.
\p 
\v 11 “Pi at hedai wo shaꞌi e nako mas am gawul wo e juh mat hekid wo e ai ihda. Hegam mo d p apꞌekam at d wabsh wo pi apꞌekamk. T hegam mo d s-apꞌekam am hab wabsh wo i chuꞌigkad ch am hab wo wa junihid g s-apꞌekam.”
\p 
\v 12 K g Jesus hab kaij, “Ab g wo ni-kaiham. S-hohtam ant wo jiwia k wo uꞌad g ni-mahkigdag mant ab wo i ha mahkhi haꞌas mat hedai heꞌes haꞌichu hab i juh.
\v 13 Ahni ani d alpha ch d omega. Id o hab d ahga ‘si wehpegkam ch si oidchkam’ ch hab d ep ahga ‘i shonkam ch i kuhgkam.’ ”
\p 
\v 14 Neh, no hig pi woho mat wo si s-ap e tahtkk ch pi wo si e el hegai mat g wehschugaj s-kehg wo wakonask, Pegih, mt hab wa masma wo si s-ap e tahtkk matp gam hu hab wo i e juh g pi ap em-chuꞌijig. Jiosh at ab wo em-mah g apꞌedag mamt ab wo koꞌad g bahidaj hegai doakag uhs ch ab wo i wahp kolhai kihjeg t ab heg eda Wechij Jerusalem. Kumt wo si s-hehgigk.
\v 15 K wabshaba am jeg ed hab chuꞌig hegam mo s-uam haꞌichu hab wua ch hegam mo hab wua g hihoina ch s-totontomkam ch ha muꞌakam ch hegam mo jijoshchud g hemajkam haꞌichu ha-nahtoi ch hegam mo s-hohhoꞌid g haꞌichu iattogi ch haꞌichu ha iattogid.
\p 
\v 16 K hab kaij g Jesus, “Ahni ant am cheha g ni-anghiliga mat am wo em-ahgi ihda wehs ahpim mam am kawod e nanmek ch ab has ni-elid. Ahni ani d Davidbad amjedkam ch wepo masma mo g si s-mahs siꞌalig huꞌu.”
\p 
\v 17 Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o ab i ha waid g hemajkam am gai ha wuhshanim hegam mo ab si has elid g Jesus Christ, Idam o hab kaij, “Ab g wo behꞌi g pi ha huhugedam doakag.”
\p Kut wehsijj hegam mat ab wo kah ihda at hab waꞌap wo chei, “Ab g wo behꞌi g pi ha huhugedam doakag.”
\p Pegih, ab g wo behꞌi wehsijj ahpim mam hedai i tatchua. Bo wa masma am em-wehhejed mo g shonkam shuhdagi am ha wehhejed g tonkkoi.
\s1 Mat ia i kuhgi
\p 
\v 18 S-e g wo nenꞌoidk ahpim mamt ab wo i kah mamt pi am hu gawul wo juh ihda gam hu baꞌich haꞌichu ahga mo in hab chuꞌig id eda oꞌohana. Muꞌi o haꞌichu in oꞌohadag g shoꞌigdag. Kut id ab wo i wehnad g Jiosh g s-koꞌok em-namkidadag mamtp ab haꞌichu wo i wehnad hegai mo in oꞌohadag.
\v 19 K in oꞌohadag mach apꞌedag matt am wo i wahp Si Hekia S-apꞌekam Kihhim ed k wo huh g bahidag hegai uhs mo ab t-chehgidch g pi ha huhugedam doakag. T wabshaba g Jiosh gm hu hab wo i juh g em-apꞌedag mamtp ahpim haꞌichu gam hu hab wo i juh id amjed oꞌohana.
\p 
\v 20 Hegai mo am s-mahch ch ahg wehs ihda o hab kaij, “Woho o wa. S-hohtam ant ab wo i hih.”
\p Pegih oi g. Ab g i hihm, t-kownalig Jesus.
\p 
\v 21 T wo wa s-em-hoꞌigeꞌel g t-kownalig Jesus k am wo em-wehmajk.
